,"enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Phong Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9GArBYIj04jNcHQTx9xu2JiqbwOyaZ-TVb2cRN3nt1snz-CSw8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Tran and her team was great! I recently switched to their practice as my current one moved me out really far. The assistant was very friendly when taking my X-rays. Dr. Tran greeted me with a smile as soon as she walked in. She made me feel really comfortable and helped me understand everything. Duyen, the hygienist, was really thorough and I left the office feeling sparkly clean! See you in 6 months!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBSfWAYyBbJRf7BBBWcM9-Xo__n68PnidLSINROc0LGSkg05o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Tracy Tran was lovely. She was kind, patient, and took the time to explain everything clearly, which immediately put me at ease. No big push or sell either. Her team were considerate and genuine, and the entire visit felt calm and well organized. The appointment was unhurried, and the care felt thoughtful and professional throughout. I appreciated the genuine attention to comfort and communication and would happily recommend Dr. Tran and her team to others.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGA9u1zsCWIH-hr_Apvy6XqFAzL1yoH-SxyBc-xExyoK24vEsGWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr.Tran is the absolute best!! She always checks in on how I’m doing throughout our service. Her bedside manner is unmatched, and is by far the best dentist I have ever been to. I leave feeling confident about my dental care both in office and at home. I highly recommend seeing her!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emma Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJVhfPDFi9xYJnh2PcsbJHtiuATCuvZ2FT38gVp4Qb-s-3u7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"During the routine cleaning, I felt what seemed like two cuts on my gums, along with noticeable bleeding. Even six hours after the appointment, I am still experiencing sharp pain in two specific spots and could taste blood in my mouth. This has never happened to me before at this dentist or my dentist back home.\n\nI don’t really care about the cut, but how it was handled rubbed me the wrong way. During the visit, I noticed the hygienist using cotton/tissue pads to press against my gums/teeth, presumably due to bleeding. I saw blood on the instrument, the tray, and could taste it, but it was never brought up by them and I had to bring it up myself.\n\nWhen I raised the concern, both the hygienist and the doctor reassured me that the bleeding was normal. I was told it was “moderate” and that it would heal, and that it may have been related to my Invisalign treatment or minor inflammation in the back. I respect their professional opinion, but I am concerned because the pain was coming from my front teeth and my Invisalign treatment ended three months ago, and I never experienced bleeding or sharp pain during cleanings throughout the Invisalign treatment period. I had pretty positive experiences here prior so I’m disappointed in how my concerns were dismissed and I felt I was really not heard by them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig Schafer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJA-izv6PUP8LWeJUTgn4YeiqaEhe84uah17pmJxhuLt_WpPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an emergency issue and they got me in quickly. Dr Johnson has been my dentist for decades. And my wife and kids have gone to him for many years. So fortunate to have a doctor like him for much of my adult life!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bee Isabella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV40XqnFmmT-PYxq19aNrq-OxNrOk1vFc4ChRKZfMlrKC1XKWZrmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really lovely. I will say honestly, I went with them because it was close to my work and covered by my insurance, but I have been incredibly pleased with how heard I have felt from my phobia of needles, to my worry about going to the dentist in general.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robin Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLg94BZn-Riv63pznQ5Ehyfkd9uA4Bx5KuLGAvuGCc48e0EHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was seated promptly. Dr. Johnson painlessly and efficiently repaired my chipped tooth, and it looks and feels great now! I appreciate the kind and professional treatment I received from Dr. Johnson and his assistant, Tamar.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harshad Barapatre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIobImZ2_dZCl_lFURSH-zxFFu7-FXfMVP2ueRpa6D8ZztPw0h=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Tran + staff are amazing and very professional. She went above and beyond to get me a referral appointment scheduled for the next day and also helped me understand my treatment options.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
