ng enough constructive life time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melanie Harig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITBNwNyvIRqr8okUwNDGTShSNg3QOV2WFi6WSHwNL_z4dYBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently saw Sam to have my teeth cleaned. She was very thorough but gentle. I felt very taken care of! Dr. Sweeney spent a long time getting to know me and my dental needs. I didn’t feel like he was rushing and was actually spending the time to get to know me! Best views I’ve ever experienced in a dental chair!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine Tomberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEI0tR6LPK8o4WfPDbXqKFVUpRqfX3x-CjTI0rsJxJ3JL2Ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Sweeney, and his staff, including Sarah and Samantha are excellent dental health practitioners! I've had my share of periodontal and routine dental work in my lifetime, going through many dental health care professionals, and I can honestly say they're the best in Washington, and equivalent to the best doctors I've had California. Dr. Sweeney and his staff of dental health professionals are state of the art in all dental specialities. They are experts in the field with attention to detail and precision, that is combined with gentle dentistry. They are all a nice 😊 kind group of people I make the effort to take a ferry ride to see every few months!!! They come highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dale Larsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWykj40siWvcE_sqSCAEu45_DhdkT2JE5_HDUWFsAQW5TPickt9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dental specialties is a very welcoming and warm environment. The staff is kind an knowledgeable. Several years ago I had an emergency implant situations and they worked  extremely hard to get me in around my schedule.  The work was exemplary and improved my smile..  They walked me through each step and made sure I was comfortable. Several years later I now go back for my bi yearly cleanings and still they are kind, caring, willing to work around my schedule.  The whole staff is amazing and I  highly recommend them for a cleaning to major dental work. Dental Specialties is the place to go!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harry Klages","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ12wRWY9yycv9Qarbp7IatydXmsKPxvsux7BBrJKUW3hTH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. Spoor for over 20 years and have more than pleased with his work over the years. Specifically cosmetic dentistry, he is wonderful to work with and I receive many compliments on my smile. I have also worked with Dr. Sweeney and have been very pleased as well. While I have not yet worked with Dr. Ansong he always makes meal feel like I'm his patient when I'm in the office. The entire staff is very competent and personable as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deidre B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEza7_WajCueY0P2Y1gc6aiOB1F8ijGBKE_xAqgkqzwnpOww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr Spoor's for many years.   I cannot say enough about how wonderful he and his staff are.  The quality of the work is fantastic, but so are the people.  They are warm and sensitive to the needs of their patients.  Sometimes dental work is uncomfortable, but it really is easier when the office feels like family.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
