 and caring. She did a crown on the lower left for\nme. It turns out great! I love it! Ty Dr. Pock for your great work! 👏\nI'm grateful to have both Dr. Starks and Dr. Pock there for my dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jean Power","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJln3LzclWUzIKPoK3m7DvhQqdZQ-GG2Cgj2slmx1pHUff6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Like others, Dr. Starks has been my dentist for at least 25 years. Always good experiences and excellent dental work. Plus thorough and patient cleanings. Same hygienist for much of my time w/Dr. Starks. Front office friendly and organized. No probs ever.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cailyn Schiltz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTeP48xbKK4zVDp1XQmp6QOkyalMmPP-cJpaEYtgNI3n7YFOuq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a great experience here! Morgan and Dr. Polk were friendly, professional, and gave my teeth an excellent cleaning. I also got some good pizza recommendations out of it! I would 100% recommend this office to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlie Maddox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYutAo74OwVbkpYmgUL9vn76wc95lTRIl4N8886vtGjT1gshMs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was a patient from 2009 to January 2023 until moving out-of- state.  The care I received from Tracy(Hygienist)and Dr. Starks was always very thorough and professional.  Highly recommend NDSD for your dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dianne Howell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcKDYexs7lIn93cAiXlMaLcT4PugbKFB9vJ_vZhIJ0v8yDyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am returning to Dr.Starks after living out of the Seattle area for 10 years and could not be happier with his advice and thoughtful concern.  His staff are helpful in every way.  The offices are immaculate,  Covid protocols are well thought out and reassuring.  Thank you for welcoming me back so warmly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kris Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwKYg0at7eQq5gUMbS_Fi8ji08p1oJxUO58rR8j8xUb4gj4aB9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Dr Stark’s for about 20 years, and I appreciate him so much. He has been the best, never had a cavity since going to him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina Ozuna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHcBY8cC8WsrIVdFDCrrtVc5_KFVqPisAd3nEAnN5q8bC89_DI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Starks and the entire team are awesome. Down to earth, thorough, and pleasant. It’s the best (and easiest) medical appointment of the year.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Douglas Hughes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8MCUY7mTuan7QUSjzCwtnX9l-BEoWCUevK1ypumCbKI3jt3ZuGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, always friendly, professional, and effective.  Have been going here for years and the cleanings and fillings have all gone well.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
