nabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Rachel Deleon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdWFyuCLZHRMcZDne69vCjrTUR7E0mBCnO2RSFhqczGvxITw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best dental office hands down, the team is so warm and professional! From the moment you walk in you are greeted with a big smile from April, she is always taking the time to go over my treatment plan and maximizing my benefits. Dr.Abu and Dr.Del Rosario are always so gentle and take the time to explain every step of the procedure. You can tell they truly care about their patients and take pride in their work. They also have an amazing assistant Hit who always takes good care of me, the warm neck pillow is my favorite part! The office is very modern and they have all the new dental equipment that make coming to the dentist very easy! Look no further this is the best dental office in town! Highly recommend!! 🦷","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandra Paredes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPkWrG4McUtTqM9TZU1mj9kq5rE1ZfTpt3fi4Ou4y339vbpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Never thought I'd find myself writing a review for a DENTIST, yet here we are. These guys are amazing, and they have truly changed my perception of what going to the dentist feels like! The team is super thorough and they have great, up-to-date equipment, so I always feel like my teeth are very well taken care of when I'm there.\n\nFrom the get-go, April and Shala make the booking, check-in and check-out processes super smooth. They have helped me book appointments over text, email, you name it. Sarah has been my hygienist most times, and she has truly been the best hygienist I've ever had. She's patient, careful to avoid hurting you, and has all the advice to give. She will give me recommendations based on my preferences to ensure taking care of my teeth feels easy, and she always remembers our conversations + progress we're making, even though I only see them twice a year!\n\nLastly, Dr. Colin is always friendly, always cracking a joke, and genuinely ensures all my questions are answered so I never leave the office wondering on what the best next steps for my teeth are. Thank you guys for taking such great care of your patients!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marianne Montrose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHOAvArmMLhnvaEFqoPjGHlHXsPK4n1E9YCz0n6vhA618hvw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. D since 11/2024 and every visit has been a pleasant experience under his care and his staff.  They are so friendly and courteous and take the time to make sure you are receiving the best care possible, as well as being comfortable during the exam/treatment.  They give the best customer service ever and their notifications are always timely for upcoming appointment reminders.  I recommend anyone thinking about switching their dental care to seriously consider Dr. D and his staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Austin Egerton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeLHrQ0TW9G1-d6zzI4MWpi0pH7Su-XiFpdj2lB6mJC25afQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Never felt so calm and welcomed at a dental office! This office truly cares about you and your dental health, taking the time to see how you are doing at every visit and making you feel right at home. The doctors are willing to work with you to make sure you get the care you need without feeling like you have to spend all your money. The cleanings are extremely gentle yet I walk away with what feels like a new set of teeth every single time no matter if it’s Shayla or Sarah! To top it all off I’ve never felt any pain or discomfort during fillings or surgery. Oh and don’t even get me started on April in the front office she is so kind and has the brightest smile every single visit! The standard has been set by this office and I don’t believe I’ll ever go anywhere else","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Edmond","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLL39cxN_d9dv8j2Ur_8h2Uibi7XyD0YboguSe6oVmldlA2C9c0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife is Indonesian and we tried several other dentists but her anxiety was just much for them to handle. Found Dr. Abu here who spoke Indonesian and we setup an appointment. He was able to talk to her and comfort her enough she was able to calm down and get her work done. I then transferred myself here too and have been working with them for about a year now. Every experience with all the employees have been excellent. I highly recommend this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_ABHo4uRDj5eaeSRHLVOwiU20qETKLYNI4mkzdq23Xa0unA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experiences at this office, everyone is kind and helpful during appointments. The assistant, Hit makes my appointments efficient and easy! The hygienists and doctor also are great at 6 month check ups!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gloria Zak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbp951cDVGGw1TNVDcqgPox2Ac1F_hSryKn_4KJKTdBdWsEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sup is the best dental assistant you could hope for.  She is sympathetic, kind, helpful and all in all, the one you want by your side at the dentist's office.  She's just so sweet.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Colbe Schicatano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJy2rdWvlDqLJOJk_6WXkMLsccihY_vkE-XcBvCJrwBfIQwuBb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quick, reliable service from a wonderful team. The office is clean and has all the latest amenities to make for a low stress dental check up.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
