more affordable (as well as payment plans)\nShoutout to Dr. Pruthi, Kayla and Tylor for helping me today! Yall were great as always :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R Carr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdzhFjh-JTGIbpBDTQAzKryIU-CcuAkOjDrwp8eADvVT3zcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a good place! Andzelikka took care of me today and it was one of the best appointments I’ve had. She was so kind and Informative it just made the time fly by. I appreciated the information she shared as well as being able to answer questions I had with further advice. The front staff was also very nice making my experience really peaceful and easy!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Jarden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDCVfViIW8k7cNmbfFQtWGXX8M4vZzqAqqgJz7x1DbTlo4__mP2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve tried a couple different locations within this network of dental offices and the Capitol Hill location is by far the best. Everyone is very kind and patient, Justin is such a friendly face at the desk and also very helpful with any questions you have with billing, payment plans, or getting your next few appointments scheduled. And Dr. Pruthi and Kayla the hygienist have completely turned my dental hygiene around for the better. I’ve always had problem teeth, but they took the time to answer all my questions, give recommendations for different routines to try, and educated me as to what’s going on in my mouth and why. I will literally travel out of my way to continue going to this office, should I ever move. They’ve made me no longer nervous or scared to go to the dentist!!! Can’t recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ChandlerDoc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8uvQXVH3_tLVaG85TlY_-sYNiJMDSnyLbMMrRHoRoCkvrfxz0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As someone with pretty intense dental anxiety and not having gone to the dentist for quite some time this team was FANTASTIC! They made me feel very comfortable and were great at explaining everything every step of the way. Without a doubt the best dental experience I’ve ever had! Dr. Koh \u0026 Justin are top class I can’t recommend them and the whole team enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randy Huynh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8TC0rliPysbBw1WvER6xNS-ThYrZ-fsA4JH8e65hOnapF6k0t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I actually accidentally had an appointment here. I was sick and asked my wife to make the appointment at Capitol Hill Seattle Dentist. But it was the best mistake ever. I'm not sure if they cost more than my previous dentistry, but the aura and effort the put in for every procedure was a step up from a lot of other places I've been. I moved away from Capitol Hill but still make time to go here because I trust Dr. Shiv Pruthi. He's a relaxing presence.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yue Ren (Kayla)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7O_KvlMaymTkkyyfa2zDP2Jt4_1AFU9X3__K26376OHAVi9kA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited here a couple of times and every experience has been great! The front desk staff are really friendly and accommodating. I had a deep cleaning and extraction with Dr. Pruthi, everything was done gentle and professionally with no lingering pain afterward - thanks for being such responsible and took time to explain my dental condition and treatment options! The pricing is more reasonable than the ones I’ve visited in Bellevue and the care is exceptional. The best dental clinics and I’m so glad I found this place :D","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
