8\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"114745123931176754682","name":"Seattle Dental \u0026 Denture Arts (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114745123931176754682"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Pike Pine Retail Core","street":"1904 3rd Ave #500","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jaymie Novey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX22JnuiVEIBnVVM6YBzPRcpKWVmGnjuPtCizXK1qwWOTKP7-py=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is a true blessing! It's a haven of warmth and welcoming smiles. Tammy at the front desk is a sweetheart of kindness and assistance. I've just undergone full extractions for my immediate dentures, and seven days post-op, I'm still navigating the ups and downs, but I know I'm in the best possible hands. The team has been phenomenal, providing top-notch care with zero judgment. They've made sure I'm comfortable every step of the way, communicating with me in a clear and compassionate manner. I've always been anxious about dental visits, but they've made the experience so much easier. I know I'm in good hands, and that's a truly liberating feeling. Today, I'm beaming with a newfound smile, and I'll be eternally grateful. Thank you to every single person who's contributed to my care. I'm eagerly looking forward to my upcoming appointments. 10/10. One more thing - they've treated me like a person, not just a patient, and that's a gift I'll treasure forever. The photo is a couple hrs after the procedure. I wanna give you an idea how beautiful they look","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1EHAivGUbol3Q_e0jEhXLrrdJl0UU1XudbIveaWEiVps6D4_pPit-dt84yyUg9p9NeOCMtSSJ5PxT7nS7zvaiP6Anap1r6kg-P3Z2S2cZvzK_jgn47_JQO9Q_xnsq1fm9lZfE2BD7dqP7g=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-29"},{"Name":"Bobby SixKiller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWstnPFMssjIaJY59ZrlE9C8Yj2allJXETce5oDZu7QiqBBpdc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been coming here for at least 5 years now. Great. Service, good people and super friendly staff. Always enjoy the atmosphere even though I am not a fan of the dentist. But this guy's are amazing.  Boris is the best. If you know, you know.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexander “Alex” H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ5RFool19tXgeB_EOUoXmKdlX5YjqAsD6jpt6aOIdzKW5IhYW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was told by the receptionist when I got there that a simple implant repair is not covered by my insurance, when it actually is.(I had the same thing done in the past, just \"glue\" the thing right back on)\n\nIf you want to avoid a pointlessly difficult time dealing with reception I suggest pursuing your dental needs elsewhere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbXUWZzaguI0rykba_4T7O7vU_5B7F0TAI_nKyZLHhYmDTZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This clinic is amazing! I want to point out how great the women who work at the front desk are, especially the one who works on  Fridays by herself, without her extreme patience and incredible work ethic, there's no way everything would go so smoothly. A huge thanks to you Ma'am!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paige N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcJ-o4orVFyBmqWbkQoiOrFqASallATXZNF_LT4mcpK9BO9hU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had such a great experience! I’m about to head out of state for school and they were super accommodating. They got all my work done in one visit and were super friendly! All of the staff there and doctors were wonderful. I can’t remember her name but the dental assistant with the blonde braids was so kind and so great at her job! I really enjoyed my former dentist back home but actually had an even better experience here. They made it very comfortable!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Selena S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWwxUIXlTwwbGWg8rU5vjyc1CbmkSlSPeVLJDkclDL1hYoi-cn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Starting a long overdue dental journey and couldn't have stumbled across a better place. Everyone so far have been Absolutely Awesome. Warm Friendly and calming environment  Starting with the Friendly security downstairs and the Wonderful Ladies at the front desk to the Great Friendly dental assistant and Awesome dentist...So far this has been Absolutely great.. for ANYONE who has underlying anxiety of dental visits.. I suggest you give these guys a try.. I'll update as the journey continues including the actual dentist that's working on me😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marmee Elizabeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-f_Bx_qBlKOZUZJ9-0mzDulePnK6Q925xW647rqn-9P3xpMq6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best dentist experience here! The office itself was very nice and clean, and the staff were incredibly comforting and reassuring. I had come in with a toothache and was feeling anxious about having a root canal procedure, but the staff made me feel confident that I would receive excellent care. The treatment went exactly as planned, and I am definitely planning on scheduling my next appointment with them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Smilgin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW538OVTizIuuzxVF73KEq-fdFacbYaC01I8Sqy2LuitnKisI1PyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am happy to recommend Dr. Park here at Seattle Dental and Denture Arts. I am 64 years old (65 in 8 months) - Dr. Park is the best dentist I have had since I was a teenager. He is patient, polite, thorough and professional. I am also happy to commend his staff / assistants, Michelle and Nilou.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
