w questions a patient might have after leaving the office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"umesh Desai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKCuDncdZ55WPYlByzK-ZmqAeaySDuusFqHNE5xsRz2Z0gyzWWYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got treatment done at 8 to 8 detal and was impressed by the systems and knowledge of the doctors there. They explained the procedure thoroughly. Their flexible extended hours worked well with my work schedule and they went above and beyond with their level of care. They are different than all other dental practices and their attention to detail and thoroughness is commendable.\nDr. Thongin is a highly experienced and excellent surgeon.\nI strongly recommend 8 to 8 to all who need dental treatment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Renzo Acosta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxTiWHr95R3HpJYkELNQQwrymWk3ouGvxyGpPncnKNs6GXjVJ_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to 8 to 8 Dental for several years  now, and I can’t recommend them enough! The whole team is friendly, professional, and genuinely caring. They’re also super flexible with my schedule, which makes it so easy to keep up with appointments.\n\nNick, the dental assistant, is always so kind and makes every visit feel comfortable. He’s great at checking in and which helps ease any nerves. Dr. Cao is amazing too. She’s gentle, thorough, and always takes the time to make sure everything is done right.\n\nEvery visit feels smooth and I always leave knowing I’m in good hands. If you’re looking for a dental office that truly cares about their patients, 8 to 8 Dental is the one!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kara Fong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvC6mZYdngXkm3FfqvEYS8DB7S8wJuLjXRFfOOVCNUgXEGBdeCMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a filling fall out just two days before a trip and was pretty stressed about it. I went to 8 to 8 Dental, and Dr. Huang really went out of his way to fit me in despite having a full schedule. I really appreciated how accommodating and understanding he was. The work feels great so far and seems like it was done with a lot of care and quality. Thanks to him, I can enjoy my trip without worrying about my tooth. Thank you, Dr Huang!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Schoen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb3UDFCS4ds5joj57zuwIMxIUMsg0BVQm3hjOXnVCktVyVPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m incredibly grateful for 8to8 Dental. Their extended hours and weekend availability make it possible for me to actually get in, even with my work schedule. The entire team is attentive, warm, and professional every single visit.\n\nDr. Thongin is outstanding. He spends real time with his patients, performs a thorough exam, and explains everything in a clear, honest way. He’s caring, patient, and genuinely committed to finding the root cause of dental issues rather than rushing into unnecessary procedures. He saved me hundreds of dollars in dental work that other offices had quoted by identifying the true problem and addressing it with a deep cleaning instead of expensive orthodontics or surgery.\n\nThe staff is equally wonderful—attentive, organized, and always providing helpful appointment reminders (which I definitely need!).\n\n8to8 Dental has earned my complete trust. I can’t recommend them highly enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXisAfFktKxwoXQocYwOvsxOFIwo8kVaWEzCTUX6_pXuMpt5aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really appreciate the doctors and staff at this dental office. Dr. Cao is gentle and knowledgeable, always so caring and patient! Sam and the staff are wonderful, making every dental visit pleasant and personal. The team works hard to offer flexibility including Sat appointments. And they are centrally located near the Capitol Hill light rail station and near bus stops. We highly recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ron Shvets","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_JaUKvFiq5Sosv2LtsM5RlxXzmndWGDC1WwNZnZZ2lt1CwVu4EQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply the best dental clinic ever! The entire staff are so warm, professional, accomodating and just awesome! Their hours are very comfortable for people working full time and you can really feel the personal care they give their patients. I've been going here for several years and even when I moved out of WA state, I still go here whenever I visit Seattle. They're that good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWa3DoA4KWL67fiI_PbiNOWYyyaU4qy3rMgVjMNeTS8wRLp3xM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very timely, flexible, and professional.\n\nDr. Huang was amazing, he was extremely thorough and asked plenty of follow up question to make sure I got exactly the treatment I need. Plus his bedside manner is great. Also received great service from his assistant Isaac, and the very patient receptionist (whose name I didn't catch)!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
