.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=128.43503\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"/url?q=http://www.downtownseattledentist.com/dental-clinic-seattle-why-choose-us/\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwiah9y6yr-UAxUMI0QIHZaSBFwQqRkIHSgQ\u0026usg=AOvVaw1OFix-uG6m87HGFWKw2H6z","source":"downtownseattledentist.com"},"owner":{"id":"104367929231874167159","name":"Gloria E. Tucker DDS (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104367929231874167159"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Central Business District","street":"509 Olive Wy #1230","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Brooke Pinkham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKw5L3pfKxMFiz46nBNWXcEyucbGPnwPr1QQdZ5rQ0S6m3tA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Thank you for allowing to provide feedback. Overall, good job on the dental work - I am liking how things are looking so far. However, yesterday was a very long appointment. It's helpful when you are able to provide detailed play-by-play on what the plan is and how long it will take. At many points during the procedure I was confused and unaware of what was actually happening with all the drills, and why numbing was needed. I am currently in a little pain in my upper gums and my nose. I assume this is normal? I was a bit in shock and unable to speak well due to the numbing of my upper lip after the procedure, in addition to being there longer than expected - which is why I didn't provide feedback at the time, nor ask too many questions. I would appreciate a call from Dr. Tucker prior to my next visit to explain the next steps. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barbara Muse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY4EwQQxNyxqe1O8Ue_F3jyGBk2KBLm7ksW9JPI3iSznn2k4CnQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Tucker is a caring dentist. I have a real fear of dentist visits and she (\u0026 her assistant) reassured me every step of my first visit. I highly recommend her expertise.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suzanne Lasser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlfp5vcvIi7cKTtjeaGyLs-CJ1DhJxG4zgfAx5tKxGN_Jp_3k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have receiving care for 25 years with Dr. Tucker. Best dentist I've encountered. My whole family gets care with Dr. Tucker: my mother and daughter.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lor G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZqj1Wd6cwzi8AR6puPSmXNoLpdh3rXytQS1ITXFJeZn6ti97_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had some bonding work done with Dr. Tucker after getting my braces off. She has the most amazing attention to detail and now the shape of my teeth look the way I’ve always wanted them to look.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine Cortis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfXmYiiIpEdXlqTAd1HdN6Ktp9nlutlw_3o7Fpx7kcZ4QKBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a long time patient of Dr. Gloria Tucker’s. I moved away and started seeing a different dentist however, upon having some dental concerns I felt weren’t being properly addressed and needing some direction on where to go, I returned to Dr. Tucker’s office.  Dr. Tucker is professional, prompt, friendly and gives sound advice.  I felt like family as my dental concerns were finally addressed.  I trust Dr. Tucker and she provides wonderful service \u0026 peace of mind (she is worth driving the extra distance \u0026 I will do so from now on)! Thank you, Dr. Tucker!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Avraham Kamara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgknQsTow6Q1B6hPX9Ftmvq31g0dxBEnNpmqs7t31ahkMJsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I broke a tooth. I called the office and Dr. Tucker treated me the next day during her lunch break with a temporary filling.\nA couple of days later, I had a longer appointment to put a temporary crown.\nWhen the permanent crown was ready, Chris called me, I came to the office in 5:30 PM on the same day, and Dr. Tucker put it in.\nThe experience with Dr. Tucker and her team, Rosa and Chris, was excellent.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hilary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN8N-_h3u_5vORjJKg9BEuCTfcwPlan6OBc6Blg8lmpaPo9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update as of 4/24/24 - I’ve been a patient with Dr Tucker for 7 years and I could not say enough great things! She is so wonderful, funny, and an incredibly skilled dentist. She really takes her time with the cleaning and makes you feel extremely comfortable. Sophia is also the best Dental Assistant and makes me feel at home! I will go to them forever. Thanks everyone at Dr Tucker’s office :)\n\n- - -\n\nI’ve been going to Dr Tucker for 5 years now and she is hands down the best dentist I’ve ever had. The entire office staff is very friendly and professional and Dr Tucker makes me laugh and feel very at ease. I also love that Dr Tucker does the teeth cleaning herself and does such a thorough job. I will continue seeing her for all of my dental needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Batya Tucker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiE8IF_WC4ZJr3-nmEos1o3WoYf6xbVusk4zPjIb4wv-GMNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was the most AMAZING experience I have ever had at the dentist office. Dr. Tucker always goes above and beyond to make me feel comfortable and I always know I am in the best care. She has such care for every one of her patients and she will cater the experience to you. I do not live in Seattle, but I go see my family there and whenever I go, I always make sure to make an appointment with Dr. Tucker. I trust no one else with my teeth at this point. The space and tools are immaculate! Dr. Tucker, her assistants and her hygienists are some of the most amazing people I have ever encountered in an office environment. I would 1000/10 recommend scheduling an appointment with her. I have had nothing but amazing experiences at her office.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
