0026h=298\u0026yaw=318.73224\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"/url?q=https://www.patientconnect365.com/dentists/washington/seattle/98122/fresh_smile_dental_seattle\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwi_maK7yr-UAxVrDEQIHZuiI7QQqRkIKCgT\u0026usg=AOvVaw0lQcPGEcOsEddg455Rn-l5","source":"patientconnect365.com"},"owner":{"id":"117715799734106650195","name":"Fresh Smile Seattle (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117715799734106650195"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Capitol Hill","street":"1801 12th Ave B","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98122","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Tallulah Lipson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEMmTJJKWd3fCXauJchRCUdMottXcLUo5IklaUoVxQ4X7jJXM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Prakash is a wonderful dentist, especially if you experience any anxiety around dentistry. My husband and I are both patients and would highly recommend Dr. Prakash. Everyone is so friendly and helpful, and the office is full of beautiful art (much of the photography was done by Dr. Prakash!). We actually look forward to our dental appointments because it’s such a lovely experience getting to see everyone! After seeing Dr. Prakash we cannot imagine working with another dentist.\n\nAs a young person I had some very bad experiences with dentistry so to say my fear level was high going into our first appointment is an understatement. Dr. Prakash has approached every appointment with compassion, understanding, and expertise. Our dental health has never been better. We cannot recommend Dr. Prakash enough.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0nng57eyRezrPH0_h5QvDM40mSWEnUBPmxTOBVwLnc4zO1ga6e-rtzqsYz1ou3DR3S5CqiMFXkjyrHkPQN666C-EhBXbRGO5ykGZJui_G5O2Sjj9HLooQgXVYWT86Bd6Z9kfcHJHwsCTVH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Jz4aHQKm2C26zAAuxa98aER2rzU0c1QAvc_JLivsNVzxfP_fI_8YRIs_gxBiN0RWuXsiQMMatrrF5y5ULZ4SBp_b6jcwJ2e3GDUOSIY1sprKLJw9yv2jbwGyzPcLmHqvutBEBcc8VHQsn=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3dKdQfCwoCOujxoMcWHk7i6iPhfNs_794qCZamoFe2NbYVPl7RDsZEz2WnmTT0QWHhk-G07iBUPvJ9jG-_hELho_TKh7X7fd26lGyeuz5RGmPzhwHIRASMsv7z2Mo5fZxbXvyoD2RLUVM=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-1"},{"Name":"Molly Pearson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1mXrn4jwZlm_ajo2GDgo5qyMkGfE-l8CJg0cS_tmGXLtcd5ki=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Prakash and his team are absolutely fantastic, hands down the best dentist I have seen. He takes the time to walk you through not just the ways you can improve your dental health but the science behind them as well. You can tell he really cares about his work and patients.\n\nI've never felt rushed or stressed while visiting. As someone who put off dental work for a few years starting in 2020, I can second what others said that even if you are anxious regarding dental visits for any number of reasons, Dr. Prakash and his team will go above and beyond to make sure you are comfortable and accommodated. The extra precaution around airborne illness safety is an added bonus as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Stavely","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOqnR3hhgNAENknlXenHxtoozAtmlnqvi3SF4sI1vkSSGqY45t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"During a routine exam, Dr. Prakash discovered that I needed a root canal retreatment (which was originally done nearly two decades ago, and I confirmed it with another dentist). He referred me to an excellent endodontist, then put in a new crown. Great service, every step of the way. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucas Monda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXmkQMpSsZaI_KY_hT4GfPurRRx6z_BfNmMxzD7wsSyP639pk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely love the dentists here. The people are so friendly and make sure you know exactly whats going on in your appointment. Great place to go for the dental purpose you need. If I could give this more stars, I would. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elaine Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb8M1rrsnn-_McSbHAptJhKsnlyWwHeAq3ohnSwPXhZm_EpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. Prakash for five years, and I have never had a dentist as caring as he. When I need a procedure that involves more than routine care, he takes time to explain why it’s needed, what’s involved, and when it should be done. If it’s something that can be postponed for a while, he willingly shared that information. Once he saved me $1000 by telling me a bone graft really wasn’t needed at all. He will take time explaining to my insurance company why they should cover a certain procedure. When I signed up for a Medicare Advantage plan and I discovered Dr. Prakash was not in its network, I decided to keep him as my provider. His care is worth every extra dollar this ends up costing me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Krista Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyPIv-EJ37S21R6kHmjPuQtDyTSXA-5dAnwdmj56HqDTbQdt1f=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed help with a chipped tooth and was seen the same day. Issue was resolved quickly and confidently by the dentist. Now my tooth feels and looks completely normal and my tongue has left it alone. I highly recommend this dentist. He has a great bedside manner and is full of wisdom.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cody Olsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2XSYCrdG4aTlJ_NOzN72JBoTaegRoFBTUqcmRQEFGOMMH6-_V=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Fresh Smiles team are stellar and kind people, yet even better Dentists. They are knowledgeable, yet easy-going, committed health-care providers, yet flexible to the realities of your work schedule.\n\nTheir waiting room alone calms me down before each visit haha. Just, top notch Dental care that doesn’t stress one out, but actually relaxes.\n\nIf you seek a Dental team, do yourself a favor and give ‘em a call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allie / A.L. Rickard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxO6CCFRkVG1_jkmHps0VIZswSbgZj3rvqIswoSDCfRv2zqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Prakash is the best dentist I’ve ever been too. Incredibly thorough, patient, and takes the time to explain his analysis/treatment plan/etc. He’s gone out of his way to accommodate my needs - it’s great his office still masks with N95s, requires patients to mask while waiting, and uses HEPA purifiers. Also appreciate the financial transparency as he is out of network with all insurance but they will bill for out of network benefits.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
