led":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Abhi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKP_VaHqpLjb4bkkzeFrHFadYRDgPL0cO818-UfKM6sS5dU03QNw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a regular at Icon Dental Center for four years and fully trust them with my dental care. From fillings and cleanings to a successful two-year teeth alignment with Dr. Sohrabi, every experience has been positive. Dr. Aboulhosn, Dr. Valentine, and Dr. Hamzey have all provided excellent care and I always appreciate the friendly conversations, and Yasmina at the front desk is always friendly and helpful staying on top of scheduling needs. The support staff - hygienists, assistants, etc and the backend finance team are all attentive and responsive, kindly acknowledging and auditing an overcharge billing issue I once found in my past records.\n\nWhile there have been occasional issues over the years, what stands out is how Icon Dental Center always listens and makes things right. That dedication has truly earned my trust and the reason why I continue to be a customer here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Knight","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnN-i-UE0VL7DQh1rbee4aT0A-nhaHnX7t7igSuj3UNxHy3SGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Icon in Seattle! The team is extremely professional, kind, and efficient. The doctor and staff deliver care at a very high level, and the whole visit feels smooth from start to finish. I especially appreciate how quick the process is—my cleaning didn’t take long at all, but still felt very thorough. A truly pleasant and stress-free dental experience. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mario Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIhDlaybz0WzLp-mi5kgYXGOZcpb8H5_zaDVjYI5ABMqincSni=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really happy I found this office. The staff is consistently friendly and professional, and the space is always clean and organized. I was looking for a dentist close to my job, and this location couldn’t be more convenient. Plus, there’s always street parking available, which is a huge bonus. Makes the whole experience smooth from start to finish.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luna Mengstab","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzyXwwZB-9-wdnoTOWcUgsHXHj4PMtONXmXi8F3pFWPEXOtw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I Had a wonderful experience at Icon. Staff was incredibly friendly made me feel like a star. Carefully and thoroughly explained my treatment plans which made me feel so confident in my decision with choosing icon dental. I normally don’t leave reviews but I had the best experience and hope everyone gets to experience it as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alyssa Maenza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw_93Y_JPLLK5oIzN3WkRRJrIX9EiSBryIjmcGTrzoQKHNovcO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone was so kind, I was able to get in quickly as a new patient and have a cavity filled in the same establishing care appointment! The dental assistant Oren was fantastic and Dr. Valentine was super funny and kind. Highly recommend establishing care with them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Lyons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbOxUQhzVACUgbqjCBET9J1C2LDHuZtC-lAyIDNIpOBzUDZB0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in for a long 3 hour appointment for fillings in my upper and lower teeth.  Absolutely blown away by the work that was done and both the Dr and technician worked together in perfect unison!  Being able to accomplish to much work in that time was truly impressive and I would highly recommend the clinic to anyone looking for detailed high quality dental work.  The office is immaculate and everyone from the receptionist at the dental clinic to the door man to enter the building were all wonderful friendly people.  Thank you icon dental clinic!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ka_7ncNSYLZhfwTZ2ocLmFwOTPm2kTmIhVsPpsKKQdtYxLwdSlTglaRSVVudkfTkUMSgANJp3KozLJXJLVCUy_yAZ_KyqG2Ne7vZS2FNyqkhvR_DtKD3cYLqFEj-Pe2wRz-qI=k-no"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Kelley Martin-Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYOpXH0EmIsC3sCQoHWvThlrBCUcDuiwB3EDGBdmnOixyaR4vo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I see Dr. Nadia at Icon Dental in Belltown. She's so fun! She is thorough with her exams, and is open to discussion for concerns. Her support staff is equally Awesome...Down to Yasmine at the front desk. I highly recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Dunaway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlFNweb0JfPYVzJ63lSBsR1o_70lVCK5TGRqVdefFDi8EzJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down best dentists and staff! My wife had her Invisalign done here, and I go for all of my checkups. Every session and cleaning has been 100% professional and high quality.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
