0_rzQvullu26UuBs65p5-cU=w224-h336-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=hNjf5tZCsaMmw6N6GCZJrg\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=237.51273\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://www.dentaltom.com/appointment/","source":"dentaltom.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"117124347508052671011","name":"Thomas McKenny, DDS \u0026 Associates (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117124347508052671011"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Central Business District","street":"509 Olive Wy #1640","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"jyoti parikh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQCUiBfclcaodKgHmy9Q-_wzOjwAAUM7-Jr9sunnMjqklQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited Dr. McKenny for a dental exam (new patient). Everything went smoothly... Front desk staff was nice and followed through with her promise to send my dental X-rays via email the same day. Dental Asst. (Andy) was efficient and gave clear instructions. Dr. McKenny himself was very nice to work with. He has a great bedside manner, is not pushy/ takes a conservative approach, and was thorough with the exam - he checked the condition of my previous dental work, any new developments, gum health / bone health, and bacterial load in the mouth. He was easy to talk to, which imo is a very important trait in this setting. I didn't need to get any work done at this time, but I would be happy to visit Dr. McKenny for my future exams/ dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVc8d-M3QgZ78R7JyJ2javuGnG-OP4tXL5kajgmUbnuZDy5ZZZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr McKenny is not judgemental and focuses on how to rebuild my teeth. My teeth were in bad shape and some were missing when I first went there. Dr McKenny has done two implants, crowns, and fillings. I have a partial denture he made and it fits and works really well. The hygienist Lee is also not judgemental and answered my questions and recommended what to use to care for my teeth.  I'm grateful for how my teeth are being fixed and cared for.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwjWWE8kev0f-j88p3LgjktHan5DBbOQ7yqCmM3XW7NiS6TYY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dentist with the best office manager and equally competent staff. 5 stars all around. I just move to Seattle recently and am so happy Nd lucky they were accepting new patients after researching all highly rated dentists in the area, Dr McKenny had an opening and I jumped at the chance. Sent my hubby first (he hates dentists) but my hubby came back with glowing reviews).  I knew I had hit the jackpot. We've been happy customers for over a year now and have had everthing from crowns, veneers, cleanings, x-rays all done with expert care. We highly recommend his office. Park next door at Pacific Place for ease.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tricia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKd0jv8LFhuk9aAcmOHIvP14XXbxkmSFVIWiUwzvaMXqjy54C8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the whole office and staff. DR.Mckenny is an awesome dentist. He is very gentle and does beautiful work. His kindness also reflects on the rest of his staff who are all spectacular. Check in was a breeze, and my teeth turn out beautifully clean every time. I have enjoyed coming here for many years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kari Zimmerman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlGLy0j7YbIUnB8_h9VuiCMpRb30anzWL95zYBYpi8TseWYEpT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First, I need to say that I am VERY high maintenance about my dentists. I have alot of dental issues due to faulty genetics and my teeth require extra TLC. After my last dentist abruptly resigned, I visited a couple other dentists who were sub-par. My first visit with Dr. McKenny was 2 hours and extremely thorough - the most thorough ever! He has done nothing but take excellent care of me and my teeth. He is great, particularly is you have \"special\" teeth like me! (I was genetically missing 14 permanent teeth). Also, the entire staff is wonderful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcLonIjm1AQaHH0TQiXTgK7c1jQgi9imtImuaDCemC_gClRTU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. McKenny is a wonderful and trustworthy dentist. He is not an alarmist. I’ve been to two dentists who told me I have cavities and they need to fill them immediately. Turns out, I don’t have cavities at all. Dr. Mckenny will not recommend a procedure unless it really is necessary. I was lucky to find his office, and I won’t be going to any other dentists. His office is welcoming and friendly, and I’ve had a great experience with all of the hygienists who cleaned my teeth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carolyn Burton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1nieoUzl1yjZ5G8rZBLGClQI8aGpb_gazergxJX2D_88xKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone was extremely helpful.  Dr McKenny and his assistant explained everything thoroughly and the dental hygienist did a wonderful job and was very caring.  The front of desk people were also very kind.  Altogether a splendid first visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elisabeth Root","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8V4UuPGdONFRq5Upj4UD92350KA_7vVM2WzZO4eY6p4yRHmhSxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr McKenny has been my dentist for my entire adult life, I've sent my husband and many other family members and friends along the way. He and Andy and all the staff are great.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
