rrison Fox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-pR7qw2asZ8VopMqFZsfb2yFVQmZufgsUSPXje92rQ0CjDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I have had the pleasure of working with Prestige for all of our dental needs. The entire team have been incredibly helpful over the past 4 years, providing great care for a variety of procedures (not limited to wisdom teeth extraction, deep cleaning and standard proactive check ups). A special shoutout to Dr Makagon, Dr Gaal, Dr Neral and Tamara for always being there for us and offering fantastic support. Could not recommend this crew enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wei Fei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLhxZQFhsZ_9UKTgQ4R_DVFvG_zCoNkuEJ921g0qcTYRMXlJ0l=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had an excellent experience with Prestige Dental over the past few years. The doctors and staff have consistently taken great care of my teeth and have been incredibly thorough, patient, and professional at every visit.\n\nThey always take the time to explain procedures clearly, answer questions thoughtfully, and make sure I feel comfortable. Thanks to their preventive care and attention to detail, my dental health has stayed in great shape.\n\nHighly recommend to anyone in Seattle looking for a trustworthy and caring dental team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A person","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLvWevlsZAPVKYYyqwUQwQ4SvoEyOrv-6DXfkENJQSMPRJ2vA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly and professional dentist. Everyone is just so nice.  I have been going to them for 10 years. They also seem to always have the latest and greatest tech and methods to make cleanings and check ups faster and better. Plus you can watch Netflix while you get your cavity filled, which helps to distract you from thinking about the work that’s going on in your mouth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"m sa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyllPcG0bhxc0JoSYWC2YttfZoMFPZR-0drXXbnSDJMr9aTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"i’ve been coming to this dental office for about five years now, and I’m truly grateful that I found it.\nIn the state where I used to live, I went to four different dentists, and only one of them was good. The other three had outdated equipment, rushed through treatments, and the dental cleanings were done quickly. I was surprised by how different each dental office can be.\nSo when I moved here, I spent enough time reading reviews to find a good dentist—and that’s how I ended up here.\n\nDr. Makagon is always pleasant, gives advice with thoughtful, patient-centered advice, provides very careful treatment, and is always professional.\nTamara at the front desk is also always thorough and helpful, and she double-checks insurance coverage to make sure everything is calculated correctly.\n\nThere was one time when the insurance company refused to cover treatment for a cracked tooth. Dr. Makagon and Tamara prepared and sent all the necessary documents to the insurance company, advised me to call them as well, and in the end, the doctor herself even called the insurance company directly to negotiate on my behalf. Thanks to their hard work, the insurance company eventually agreed to cover the cost. Both the doctor and Tamara always go above and beyond.\n\nThe office is clean, and all the staff members are kind and welcoming. I’m really glad I found such a good dental office. Having had unpleasant experiences with other dentists before, I can say with confidence that this is a great dental office—they do things the right and provide excellent care!\n\nI went in today for a small cavity treatment, and the doctor worked so carefully and thoroughly that I was really impressed.\nThank you, as always!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miguel Valarao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyd706wsH-hVrn4jgzRkx7wA0ejNU9xSqIAJCFydD-ysujYNqz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Prestige Dental for the past two years. By far the best dental service I’ve ever gotten. They’ve helped me a lot to improve my health across the board — wisdom tooth extraction, Invisalign, implant surgery, general cleanings. 100% recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsD47xtJTYXByto14XNYZ9hchUqOnV7ZlpyVTpzQrIF4T9_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Prestige Dental for about a year now, and every visit has been a great experience. The team is always friendly and professional. I’ve gotten the Airflow cleaning a few times now, and it’s been amazing — super gentle and leaves my teeth feeling clean and smooth. It is the most comfortable cleaning I’ve ever had. You can tell the team genuinely cares about their patients and takes pride in what they do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWcRRcWAywBaPCE0VtYXPmgxxqBoOjF4lnHtzdkoj_6rUOUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First of all, I DON'T RECOMMEND this place at all.\nThe front desk and the dentist are having a very weird relationship and they are just trying to recommend excessive treatment. They will tell you how poor your teeth are, how many treatments you need to going through. At least go to a second opinion to make sure you are receiving necessary treatment.\nIn addition to this, they charge $100 for appointment which is ridiculous. I have never seen a medical service doing this. You can charge no show fee though.\nLast but not least, they are trying to sell you a specific brand of toothbrush at outrages price. I forgot the detailed number but much more expensive than Costco. No matter the price, they should not be allowed to do this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelley Spranger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_Tzzh-fTm0i7Zjko1bvzxwgX-WwesotRC8Nc8Z3WC8iBbug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the absolute best experience and would highly recommend anyone see Dr. Salha. Everyone is extremely kind and he listens to your concerns and priorities as well as factoring in new research and studies. Not a rushed experience at all an he really focuses on your goals and how your mouth hygiene impacts your overall health. So excited to be established here!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
