le":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHJpOwfW2WwtJWRPEiglwKJZKXYsmzK51ER8Zb25hWiOOaQI-kUdLok-HY2-CWxwKWWJCWXMx0hIgXqbbwNSDWbiFTao8halo6BzWRT06PKBoJtGd427Ryja6iuy7XfJxua1A7V-YaE9HJX=w449-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=XbaCP4qn7drkRYuNuDIL1g\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=154.77676\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://booking.dentologie.com/booking","source":"dentologie.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"104390788919165340031","name":"Dentologie - Capitol Hill (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104390788919165340031"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Capitol Hill","street":"1530 Melrose Ave","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98122","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Destiny Montgomery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuzWeUoEZXYdFDhMyQzwQ6Pn3y-hoIW-Q34fFjScLI-42lrqM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first visit at Dentologie 2/13 and it was honestly such a great experience. From the moment I walked in, Nathan at the front desk made everything feel smooth and welcoming. Check-in was easy, and I immediately felt taken care of.\n\nMy hygienist, Zohreh, was so gentle and thorough. She explained what she was doing, checked in on my comfort, and made the cleaning feel calm instead of stressful. I really appreciated how attentive and kind she was.\n\nDr. Hina Jaffer was wonderful, professional, knowledgeable, and easy to talk to. She took the time to explain my dental health clearly and didn’t make me feel rushed or judged. I felt heard and supported in the whole process.\n\nStephan, the dental assistant, was also great very attentive and made sure I was comfortable throughout the appointment.\n\nOverall, the whole team worked seamlessly together and made my first visit feel easy and reassuring. I’m really glad I chose Dentologie and would definitely recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leslie Casias","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKVgyCiPGuWxPHGOqzBJHgXDezf4trMKewQa1uP73Gadu6hIS82g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first visit at dentologie today.  At check in, Nathan was warm and informative.  I did not wait long to be brought back by Allison, who took my X-rays.  She was like kind and gentle working around the mouth. Dr Jaffer was very knowledgeable and explained my plan of care throughly.  She took the time to answer my questions.  She is very personable which made me feel confident in choosing to continue my care there.  Highly recommend this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Greenwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJyPOAjmRW7pr39HwtIZCqztB0YchvjOhprbo4G9o1vttUdQv2gw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very understanding, kind, efficient from front desk to dentist to out the door. Fit me in for an emergency visit for a chipped tooth. Walked through step by step by Dr. Jaffer so knew exactly what to expect. Even with a temporary crown no one would know it was not my original tooth. Very pleased.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ting Wei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2N0kYkTyrZKvj6pLZYuXvLOQTXPpCinaH4UYGW8D-hEHR6fXbvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited Dentologie last month looking for a more convenient location, as I’ve seen my regular dentist for years but they are quite far away. My experience here was deeply concerning. After an exam, Dr. Jaffer informed me that I needed crowns on four of my back teeth due to decay. Rather than showing me X-rays, she used a 3D scanner to point out dark lines on the surface of my teeth as proof of the \"decay.\"\n\nDistressed by this news, I went back to my long-term dentist for a second opinion. After a thorough exam and X-rays, it was confirmed that those \"dark lines\" were simply minor stains, not decay. There was absolutely no need for crowns. I am shocked that I was nearly pressured into a permanent, invasive, and completely unnecessary treatment. Please be very cautious and always get a second opinion before committing to major work here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Madeline Zsuffka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPcVNGrKc6YMRAkRQPqzSIv41_VRdtuv_3hKpzeheok0CsQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Dentologie! The whole team was welcoming and made the visit super easy and comfortable.\nDr. Ruchi Patel was thorough and kind, Zohreh was wonderful during my cleaning, and Nathan at the front desk was super helpful and friendly.\nReally appreciate the care and professionalism from everyone — highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aniyah Jordan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2mweoOf8sH_VUOwjYEThLc23N4ahcVtyXXAIpz59nBIM64Y-1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice clean office. The staff is all super friendly and very helpful/accommodating. I also almost never have to wait upon arrival. Would 100% recommend! Thanks Dentolgoie Team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Claire Howard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSwROtlwj9mrExevGEkwaQkY8ZwgvZG5r7d-Z-Rd57ofhN2g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Carl had excellent bedside manner and Dr Patel gives me hyper competent vibes, all in a cozy atmosphere.  Big fan, easiest dental appt I’ve had, will be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erica Gamet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIMVHEVJQiJ9aprcdjoKF3TwH2Tf4YtXs1t5WU_IlfQ_Y4axY5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff, hygienists, and dentist (Dr. Jaffer) in a laid-back atmosphere. Went there for an emergency to start, but they are now my go-to dentist. Easy bus and walking access in Capitol Hill.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
