rcontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNH8-fRXvmSE0Loc2QepRbqz2tw9fG43BgcSHlHRctN3xs8nI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Probably the best dental visit I’ve had. Nice, calming atmosphere, warm greeting and a gorgeous view of Seattle from the 17th floor set the stage for a painless but thorough exam and cleaning. I highly recommend Skyview Family Dentistry!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DENNIS ADAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJA8CG850PiokIPzgJJCPx3qE4p046NScadA2k28adUx5oMXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had excellent service from SkyView Dentistry. Cleaning and a filling have been carried out promptly and courteously. I can highly recommend this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"F G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLsPvBPI2x2WzrtsZwQEaFZiRv2_vPoeM8Y1thuSoXYXXRJcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my 2nd experience as patient and I was quite nervous. I saw Dr Relan on March 7th at Boren office to start the dental work to have a crown on one of my front teeth. Two weeks later it was complete. I’ve had many crown works in the past at different dental offices.  I strongly believe this is the best crown work I ever had. I can’t be happier. She’s one of the best not to mention she was very caring as well during the entire procedure and beyond. Her office staff always available to help if I needed one. Thank you all","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joanna Bolas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOcbUxjXqNBDb1Rg-HV7nE4yLbtnSOhhGm7FpVIigsc_GnOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"switched to skyview family dentist due to my previous changing their  accepted insurance. I have had some gum issues so dental cleanings are always a bit sensitive, Dr Soni did a very thorough cleaning while listening to my limits. the view from the office is nice too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vineet Somwanshi","ProfilePicture":"https://