ive. I had a filling come out that needed to be replaced with a crown, and they got me in immediately so I could take care of it right away. They’re always upfront about costs and respond to any questions I have within a business day, which I really appreciate. It’s rare to find a dental office that’s this thoughtful and efficient. I’d recommend them to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQoTJ5Og37L5Jia3epW2iGb_h7yyaVX1JASKi1AS7kfAK19N8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming here for the last 2-3 years. Dr. Mulye and his team are so kind and thorough. They are also non-judgemental and never try to sell me anything. Shiori is so kind and hard working as well! We love this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roberto Panora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXt25U6ZfRuSmdvmP1FbrKcFlZrLuyVLFF0N5z484SM7DIGTl0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When first moving here I spent hours reading Google reviews trying to find the best dentist. I ended up choosing Pinnacle Dental care and I am super happy with my choice. Dr. Mulye not only has a vast knowledge of dentistry, but also clearly takes the time to explain your diagnosis in a down to earth way.\n\nI highly recommend his practice, and I have even recommended some prospective dentists to consider seeking opportunities to assist and learn from Dr. Mulye. It is clear he is running a tight ship but also while fostering an atmosphere of learning and support that extends down to those that work for him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Opicka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYZGwgXVPPo4y15pKNQZTqu6MWwhTO5ZY9cbgtwWAKJGXHFpNf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dentist and dental technicians. Came in with a laundry list of things to have done and after six months Dr. Tejas Mulye and his team fixed my mouth. Very friendly office and very accommodating. I would highly recommend if you’re looking for a dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Don Minor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWORGf1ets-pGp96FPASlH74-eSz4yieo1DsCcr6PuOxOspg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are in need of dental care, I highly recommend Dr. Tejas Mulye of Pinnacle Dental Seattle.  I have spent the past few months having long-neglected issues with my teeth attended to by Dr. Mulye, after finding him by chance.  Both he and his staff were professional, nonjudgmental and friendly in their approach, as well as very accommodating of my special needs.  Procedures used, which included a root canal and crowns, were always thoroughly explained in advance of and during their occurrence, so I never felt as though I was being caught off guard or misled; and, the results were as expected and desired.  Therefore, I could not be more pleased with my experience at Pinnacle Dental Seattle.\n\nDon Minor, Seattle.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mimi Sanchez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu6ePlFqeET16HhZMTGBs0GZMlr-bm6NmnYjTlFUhWSm8ns3mY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have pretty bad dental anxiety, so going to the dentist is never something I look forward to. After a really unpleasant experience at my last dentist in Seattle, my partner recommended Pinnacle Dental Care, and I’m so glad they did.\n\nThe staff here is honestly wonderful. They got me in for an appointment in a very reasonable amount of time, and from the moment I arrived, everyone was super kind, non-judgmental, and just really accommodating. They even asked if I wanted to use the WiFi while I waited, which was such a thoughtful touch.\n\nThe dental assistant was incredibly kind and made me feel comfortable right away. That made a huge difference for me. They also gave me some helpful tips and techniques to keep up with my dental care at home, which I really appreciated.\n\nOverall, I can’t recommend this place enough. If you’ve had bad dental experiences in the past or just want a kind and professional team, this is definitely the place to go.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danny Falls","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVm8ejnUkhYp-_B-JmFOZ1iDl2VcvCoqdBeFgr_hpfHOEdcThScCw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Pinnacle! This is a new dentist for me and I have a complex dental history. Dr. Mulye was able to schedule an appointment for a checkup within a couple of weeks of calling when other dentists were booked several months out. Even better, they offer appointments on Saturday twice a month, which works great with my busy schedule. Office was clean and staff were professional and friendly. I've had A LOT of dental work and I can say this was one of my most pleasant experiences yet. Thank you to everyone at Pinnacle!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexander Sydat Bang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1PjdQNskrBY0YMjU4iHTinvfKPPqzV07HVmWj0KZmKsSxgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding care and service - I came here after going to a corporate dental office who recommended I get a mouth guard, 2 inlays, deep cleaning - very unusual for me. So glad that I came here for a second opinion. Dr Mulye relieved my concerns and did my dental cleaning / filling so smoothly. Would recommend this practice and Dr. Mulye without hesitation!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
