ere is kindness from the time I walk through the door until I leave. My husband has gotten a few crowns \u0026 he is always pleased. It is so nice to know I'm getting the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"G G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI342yP-a6ZZ7ez0Sxocn9ukPUqqOPoLQQQwNVkL36PtPzWHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. Pavinee's for over 5 years. She is the best! I am very satisfied with the crowns, cosmetic bonding, and other work she has performed on me. It is also great that she is a kind, compassionate person. This past week I had an appointment with Tricia, the practice's new dental hygienist. I found her to be conscientious, gentle, and thorough. I highly recommend this dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bmoni smart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIcJmHICcFOyUs23DWfaEhJ_ow6EX-0hCdJm-CNjXfl5_Qow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great folks! Quality work. Need to improve on insurance checking. Some work needs to be done, they send estimate, they say they will check with insurance and the check with insurance disappears.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wendy McPhetres","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULQwjvwbwxGAL5MA9uEOCUFfYh9fq7xXX21OPTBnEdEXpuGzY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient at Seattle Specialty for 45 years!   Through the years and through the inevitable changes, the care for their patients is top priority.   They are vigilant at monitoring changes in my mouth and taking appropriate steps to improve my oral health.  The staff is personable and care about their patients.   People often ask me why I travel so far to the dentist....and my reply is that it feels like home when I'm there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ann Mahony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKac9SoWMqS52BiICUOjQ2pMpi6edRPpjmvWiS4zUO2ZnprpA=s120-c-rp-m