"image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGVOFT_iFDMl5xAqbCKgzw-Mj71ka103wQVM5ejNmmOeIN0FacGxN2epHA3bqEC5nzanXkb9Tvgp3Rh8qpBUf0G1H8X3QND704BULZZTMT2Suvt4Q9esCxEs_C1BE3voNdXi7ir=w224-h398-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAG8P4ROO2s21SwG9gYzF1a6IKA4-R4B6zP0CdcGz0I-7d9Nu0jQ0eXyXB-s7L-f1BtRuv9QfmzA9W6k9y-D9dRoCXTeKPGsutdNoBMHI7BnnZdGlJ14HJjvTAbVEWmtRx5gqxFl5lb0vbNF=w238-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=V1myslymy2HYm4gkOMeWgg\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=108.99796\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://booking.dentologie.com/booking","source":"dentologie.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"114233827062227936797","name":"Dentologie - South Lake Union (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114233827062227936797"},"complete_address":{"borough":"South Lake Union","street":"124 Westlake Ave N","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98109","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jogiel Piñero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoAjcphzkpxHfB3w8lbVyVp-kh6uvipONfva-7tlwKqUfrMc87=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my first visit at Dentologie to see Dr. Shawna Sarrett, all I can say is Ive never been to a dental’s office where you do feel at home and at ease.\nAlma in the front desk is really nice. Which makes everything easier. Also, I recommend to complete the forms before going in so the process go smoother and faster for you.\nDr. Sarrett is incredibly amazing, she’s literally the best dentist I’ve gotten my teeth done with. Very knowledgeable and very professional and fun at the same time.\n\nI was so worried about my tooth, I thought I was gonna lose it, but Dr. Sarrett saved it and I couldn’t be more thankful.\n\nI highly recommend this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Merline Souvenance","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcogB82bduRwJgqn6qBvH8kgS7vqYhntjlvY4wqgKd70tZC5b7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a really good experience going to the dentist, especially since it had been a while since my last visit. I was honestly a little nervous, but everyone there was so kind and welcoming that it made me feel comfortable right away. When they found out I’m going to dental assistant school, they were really supportive and encouraging, which meant a lot to me. It was actually really nice to be able to see how everything works from a professional point of view and connect what I’m learning in school to a real dental office. The whole team was very cool about it and made the experience even better. It reminded me why I’m excited to be in this field.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCYZT86SmC1NygA2VDFH8jhKZGgLDtIbFuvleOQRHzo0zp78xm7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit - such a wonderful experience! I've been looking for a new dentist and found the one! Everything was easy - from scheduling online and getting my paperwork in electronically, and then the visit itself couldn't have been better.   I love the technology and how wonderful the team was.  And I even got a goodie baggie full of good things!  It's been quite a while since I've received one so it all added to a great visit.  Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs2qQnCDir4B70lB5-r1Kh-_Q2E2M_y6wKOq2WBt1va0Z14Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone who helped me at Dentologie SLU today was truly amazing. I came in for an emergency visit feeling extremely anxious after having a broken tooth exposed this week, knowing it would be a gamble whether everything could be fixed in one visit. I am so incredibly grateful that the team made the time—nearly three hours—to create a temporary crown for my broken tooth and even take care of a cavity on the tooth behind it.\n\nDr. Kerre was so patient and kind, especially when I wasn’t taking to the anesthesia right away. She made absolutely sure the left side of my mouth was completely numb before starting, which helped ease my nerves so much. My hygienist Zuhal was wonderful and made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire appointment.\n\nAlma at the front desk was also incredibly kind and helpful when walking me through the financial side of things. Everyone communicated clearly, answered all of my questions, and genuinely made me feel cared for. I couldn’t be more thankful for this team and highly recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kit Trainer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCkXGyHKLp9YOJHwC0xVEgksmdBJvPKPUOLLCO3lRjBZh2w9ec=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love dentolgie. Every hygienist I’ve had has been wonderful and so is Dr Kerre! They make scheduling a breeze and cleanings are always comfortable yet thorough. Also Alma at the front desk is very helpful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Flora L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_Ziw7JrdFT8tK44hf-mx7oEMRnIHWTfqZQM--Fakw1yBw_zLXRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Modern, clean, and uses the latest technology to examine teeth! I am so happy that I found my dentist in Seattle. I couldn't settle on a dentist in Seattle for a few years because of outdated offices and discrepancies in dental consultations. But I can finally settle here! They have the nicest smelling office, the friendliest staff, the comfiest dental chair with faux leather, and the newest technology that examines everything about your teeth and gums. I now have a full scan of my mouth and I feel confident that my dentist knows every detail about my mouth through this scanning technology.\n\nThey also have TVs facing front and on the ceiling! The \"gift\" they gave me at the end of the visit was the most variety I've gotten from a dentist in my 30+ years of dentist experience.\n\n1000% recommend this dentist to anyone!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1OtnZpUBAtaacRTO1JzB_diHm9stmkjjcoeAGHkvUU5O_V0aS1EfTIGJ3bJDcL145c6nKB32SKPHJRADDex0oVMzxfzukGlJOurssVgLdsRaoALKaQ8GkSR_vX0lv6jgSbKGkV=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1vqJRglspQOivZLZaZsLLAiFU4y_rjcAyfmIsoKoAvpXyls8l8n4gHF32GITdVeSwjmiFae_gitewdzVmy3pI_LV8FUdrR9uDDJK8S7JM0H1G7i-CwgHODVlUXxGGNSEZ50JG-=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0yvEqOSXo5PNjwS9soRGw6jITzwyz_mRc-2ny-a7-F3cqpPzxK9DCSsc18vnWuLl8XEwobcX7hBGvoYRIGErIKp4WuyAdbtOCBEiobCEFRLuYGfl_tE9KVGwuZMe5dnErRqu-d=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3I-uyx3tHLSqhkQ6Qs1bsQAeyEr7M5k1lbBszUGeiTaDX-OeokrEx5Joh4pbRBHqqN6IajHLM3e2XLowZ98NBcgnjynsnCPjphaWdh1ekHthTDQOAxDE2YGSjmKzrRgqlake0=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Javaria Yousuf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZb_LfkM0ZvQQmmZea6JGY1tP69NVpnJYuNXPVuPCrX5B91HQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kerre did an excellent job with my invisalign transformation. Thank you to Alma, Zuhal, Farrah, Mignon, and all the other Dentologie SLU staff for creating a seamless and comfortable experience for their patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Kord","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7Xlc-ZO-mZnd9l6fFqx_Uan1xAlMGiaoVkX2ooLYHI2Or2TzD0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's nice how knowledgeable and friendly the staff is here. They readily answer questions and the TV to show me my xrays while they explain treatment plans is comforting. Almost 2 years going and no complaints yet!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
