ly upon arrival and Dr Deborah is very professional and has a gentle touch. My teeth feel super clean after the dental visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob Deane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaY9RsEbzN8RkCcPygXxpwtg8BFbZlFU43B4zg0IEaXoMmpw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Jeffrey Lee and Beverly treat you like a member of the family.  Their expert dental and personal care is truly appreciated.  I recommend Second \u0026 Vine Dental highly, without reservation!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hans Welz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVJK9LouGyMjM7Bv2SX9vINvtS4ktaVaTHc70Vi4EEHg4pjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent work again. Just had a cracked tooth with a crown fitted and a chipped tooth recappt.\nDr. Lee performed painless and excellent dentistry and has the warm endorsement of my entire family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Scullin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWhNczrgl7X87UGwkOC2DfWrQ2TfxpaEiOeuT9OCgVRZZjjEvV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the most thorough dentist in all of Seattle, who actually listened to me and took my concerns seriously. I found them through Zocdoc and got in right away which can feel like the service will be hit or miss. Instead, I got a complete analysis of my teeth and gums and bite with the most modern technologies I’ve seen so far in Seattle. We have a real plan to treat my issues and he made sure I understood the plan and how it was phased out. He also recommended a specialist for TMJ pain I’ve been having for years and I led the office crying in relief that someone had finally listened to me and found a way to help so I’m not in so much pain all the time. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carol Farr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJg5tWQntfb5TvQXmyFQ1Y1zaGT3F7DodwilIlRsecsz2z16g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr.  Lee is great.   He made my front teeth look beautiful.   This Endue office is very nice and I feel I am in excellent hands.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wendy Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJz_oJVMGkzsC0QOjIC1szCi13p1n1VQbR_Rxg78J2O6B9uQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wish I had discovered this dental office (2 blocks from my apartment in Belltown) when I moved here in 2019. Instead I went to 2 different dental offices in the area, both of which were truly off-putting. While high end with furniture and art, they really didn’t focus on patient care.  1st). Being scolded by a dental hygienist in a truly condescending manner ( ii am in my 60’s and take care of my teeth); 2nd) listening to the doctor and the hygienist talk about their designer label at purchases at the Bravern in Bellevue while they worked on my teeth.  I had enough!\n\nI stumbled upon Dr. Lee’s office last year and thought I would give it a try. Like I said, I wish I had found them back in the day. Both Dr. Jeffrey Lee and Dr. Deborah Lee are just the best. They take the time to explain everything, including taking pictures so one can actually see what they are talking about. The cleanings were comprehensive and thorough. The procedure I received was phenomenal. Dr “D” (Deborah) even tested my gums after the Novocain to make certain I was fully numbed. Everything was explained as it was happening so there were no surprises. It was the best dental procedure I have ever had which is saying a lot since I suffer from dental anxiety. They really treat their patients with kindness and respect, and went above and beyond for me when they found out I was losing my job and my insurance at the end of the year. They treated me like family instead of a patient\n\nTheir office lobby is well appointed and cozy so they put their focus on dentistry not the aesthetics of designer chic. (Great magazines that are actually current!).  You are greeted at the door by a kind and helpful receptionist, Beverly.  She will work with you on short notice.  She will also make any financial responsibility on your part very clear up front without pressure to have something done. There is no upselling here—just good, honest dentistry.\n\nThe entire office is spotlessly clean and welcoming. I cannot say enough good things about Doctors’ Lee and staff, but I can say this—if you live in downtown Seattle and/or Belltown, or anywhere in the Seattle area—this is the dental office to choose.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGvL3fec7Htouuiz_tQ1ehvbHix4pEQ8SPD3EBujykZZS9Ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very skeptical at first after reading some of the reviews. I went in and was honest about cost concerns and talked with Dr. Lee. Not only did they all take the time to see me and walk me through every step of the process but they treated me like a human and not just a number in a business.\n\nCompared to other dentists in the area I recommend you give them a chance. The team there is excellent, they are people too. They may not have the fanciest gadgets but they make sure everything is perfect. Dr. Lee has a passion for painting and arts, and it shows. They took quite some time just to make sure they chose the proper color of filling.\n\nAgain, I highly recommend giving them a chance. I don't think you'll regret it. I will personally be going back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anthony Anthony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLf1_U8oAMrL7-lpIiCzeB7GMRSAq_eANjpSjWFoauY9jt-Fw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the front to the back second and Vine dental was an amazing experience great doctor great assistant and great front desk. I felt comfortable relaxed and the dentist Dr.Paul alota did an amazing job his assistants did amazing job. The price was right great deals fantastic equipment nice and clean. If you're looking for a fantastic dentist, you will love it.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
