me":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Karen Berndt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvdv9x6HunZ5D9V_x7zW_5TznBiJ55n2rcvKBQlMQiOqEugUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Domova and Sarah have been great. They are precise to get everything from color to bite correct. It was a relief to find someone who takes my insurance\nplan and the office staff dealing with what’s covered and what’s not is tricky at times.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3crg9KtAG-zCR_Gd6wi0U_St_deJwZ_A-IxpKb30nMO5rt_gal9yTuY-GgJyrYmpI7EqAwE4D4DHNfwKmBB4CHf295hFpt9EtKeTHCF_Nx7ATLr1dU0JDeronSAGeW4yN2BMeSz7J8_b11=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-23"},{"Name":"Iryna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMpb04lmr5ztevZmB2Jfsy1eRBtH1NYmE9H8Okav2E4vBGDobu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"\"I am truly grateful for the exceptional care I received from Dr. Dimova. She is an incredibly knowledgeable and compassionate dentist who takes the time to explain every step of the treatment with patience and kindness. From the moment I walked in, I felt completely at ease thanks to her warm and professional manner. The results exceeded my expectations, and I couldn't be happier. Thank you, Dr. Dimova — you are outstanding at what you do! I wholeheartedly recommend her to anyone looking for top-quality dental care.\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rajat Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOuqTmRoLHBMfpmWpL4cc4OIlky507zY3cJgUpsMgz8PvFm2ZP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’m writing this review after a disappointing experience surrounding my recent wisdom tooth removal appointment at Bell Harbour Dental. I want to be very transparent so future patients know what to expect.\n\nI had an appointment scheduled for a wisdom tooth extraction, but at no point before the procedure did anyone send me the treatment plan, insurance breakdown, pre-op instructions, or any details about what to expect. I received no communication — not five days before, not the day before, not even a reminder with the required prep steps.\n\nWhen I called the clinic on the day of the appointment to ask for the treatment plan, the staff acknowledged they had missed sending it. Despite admitting the oversight, they still insisted on charging me a $75 no-show fee, even though my request was simply to reschedule and receive the treatment plan properly this time. I actually wanted to continue with them — I wasn’t trying to avoid the appointment — but instead of taking accountability, the front desk staff were rigid and seemed more focused on enforcing fees than supporting a patient who never received the necessary information.\n\nUnfortunately, this is not the first issue I’ve had with the non-doctor staff here. On previous visits, especially for my cleaning, the hygienist seemed very casual and unprofessional. She was cracking jokes with colleagues and chatting during my cleaning while I was lying there with my mouth numb and uncomfortable. It didn’t feel like they took patient care seriously, especially considering how much they charge.\n\nThe only positive I can highlight is Dr. Domova.\nShe is excellent , very knowledgeable, articulate, and genuinely cares about her patients. She explains everything clearly and makes you feel heard. It’s unfortunate that the quality of care and professionalism outside of her does not match her standard.\n\nOverall, my experience with the administrative and support staff felt disorganized, unprofessional, and profit-driven, with little transparency for patients. I hope the clinic takes this feedback seriously, because with better communication and more professional staff, experiences like mine could be avoided.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Philippe Rosier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpR6pyJhhD3ZTKo2a3TSmOl6kJDy36j1MKnwmsZCFODB2UPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From moving a lot from city to city and having various dental issues, I’ve had a fair share of dentists throughout my years, but Dr. Dimova is a JEWEL. She moves with subtle speed, her steady hands give quick \u0026 painless Novocain shots, and gets the job done seamlessly. Simultaneously, she has an uplifting spirit day in and day out… never seen her any other way.  No question in my mind, I highly recommend Dr. Dimova. Also, have to give a shout out to Kelea (Dental Assistant) \u0026 Mya (Hygienist) for being cool, calm and focused… and also laughing at my jokes. Front desk is a rotating slough  of professionals, courteous, and easy going individuals 👏🏼👏🏼🤟🏼","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVis0DPqsHH6prhLtM-JfNmWcL6W1eScC1GPtjubqMK5LSe8rM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The dentist is great, but the office operates in complete chaos. I was charged based on the wrong treatment plan created by staff, paid my balance in full, and months later began getting nonstop texts and emails demanding more payment for their mistake — honestly, they’ve contacted me more than a crazy ex. Despite multiple requests, Nicole refused to escalate my concern, and when I was finally connected to the manager, Boma, she claimed the owner agreed I was responsible for their error. It’s unprofessional, disruptive, and completely lacking accountability. They seem to run the place ad hoc with no rhyme or reason. Sad to say I won’t be back — read recent reviews and watch out for surprise balances.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"likith nujella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5JhWHlhxgON-t4ClOsx09m2dEtrwiKpHHUaOMIeNwcrT1jw-SHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m honestly very happy with my experience .The doctors were patient and explained everything in a way that was easy to understand. The staff was friendly, and the hospitality was top-notch. I felt cared for from start to finish.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anastasiia Lukasheva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn9hDBEtt9u7Arrn4gp6mg06xZqQzmlwkclTKAL8lFNy9G8QZS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love my  Dr. Radost Dimova! If you get an appointment I highly recommend her. I’ve been to many dentist and she is certainly the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Moe Ghasemi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAZ41SmDEy1USoLsWbVfkdD6lyX9oUxIBWErY_zM5qlkIJX67m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really love this dental clinic, all their staff are kind and attentive, dr Dimova is the best dentist i have ever had.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
