dozens of clinics for various medical procedures for about a month.  more than half never responded at all. most of the responses did not address my direct questions.  She gave me all the info I needed up front \u0026 I had a great experience with Baja Dent.  Thank you for making this work.  I was ready to give up","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"elliot walter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8kzsIccIiXVwn9Ff-ah6CZuFsprTXSdOJNv2z76Z2ghjenuAd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"So I began working with Dental Departures and Haniel a few years ago when I needed to have my teeth worked on because I’d had cancer and radiation which ended up rotting out a good portion of my teeth…I started working with a clinic recommended down in TJ Mexico… This happened over the course of 2-3 years but it soon became apparent that I needed to do something about all my teeth….the clinic in TJ was just way beyond my budget financially so I got back in touch with Haniel, he did some research and recommended a clinic in Istanbul Turkey who were able to do everything I needed done and for a price that I could afford to do…Haniel coordinated with them and myself to work out the logistics and all the details where I was going to stay, picking me up from the airport, picking me up every day from my hotel, taking me back to the hotel, providing medication for pain, inflammation and things and so much more…there were a few minor glitches that came up but got them fixed and worked out so overall I was very happy with the process and the outcome of my new zirconium teeth..Thank you Haniel and the team at Renova","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OChn8m0Uh21RZi1uIMEik7fJ2GLe0XPIIFIC7iKtZ1gqvDLNear2Pgn0JYDpxygyLYQutMZDZPmuHbS2hyT7YV8eJNxxpznXQ1X22LXoXFKTstfJ_ZJ4ZijgE2Q-YDk0IcE4-rdFYvE_J=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3lBJldwVv7xBzxWcln3fYrbuRwMiSJxLRthWtP4WNMS1hDs82rWP87zIt1EzirXorIF3ObSOg4xR6m4Q3d8uziAWOGfK