order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101426690181446806185","name":"Tseng Cindy DDS (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101426690181446806185"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Central Business District","street":"600 University St # 808","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kevin Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRKHSkyvz0OG2gjDkRNH2dq4k2zfcuJ4wViZwXgXLXM07673og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Dr. Cindy's office for a while now and always recommend it to anyone new to the area.\n\nDr. Cindy takes a super conservative approach to dental care, which I really appreciate. I've never felt pressured into getting procedures I don't think I need, and that's a huge relief.\n\nThe hygienists are also incredibly friendly and welcoming. They make you feel at ease, even when you're getting a cleaning. And the office staff is always helpful, especially when it comes to referrals to specialists. They've connected me with some great docs when I've needed extra care.\n\nOverall, I'm really happy with the care I've received here. If you're looking for a dentist who prioritizes your needs and doesn't try to upsell you on unnecessary work, I'd definitely recommend Dr. Cindy's office.\n\nBonus: great views from the 8th floor!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Zaretzky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTSjtsunz9gsRMI-rzOmJBUBVeh3yuKai4PaK1qPKWt-SdwA8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited the dental office of Dr. Cindy Tseng, for the first time last week. I found them to be professional, efficient, and very friendly. From the moment I walked into her office, Lindsey, the receptionist, made me feel right at home.\n\nThe first thing they did for me was to contact my previous dentist who had neglected to send my records. Thankfully this saved me from many x-rays.\n\nAmy, the dental hygienist, did an excellent job deep cleaning my teeth. She was extremely concerned with my comfort during the procedure.\n\nDr. Cindy Tseng is a very friendly people person. I am always nervous around medical professionals, but she made me feel comfortable enough to easily discuss my concerns with her.\n\nI would highly recommend that you visit Dr .Cindy Tseng and her dental team. I have had a great experience with them, and I'm sure you would be impressed also.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yessenia Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_RksAO-gjaImTywKJnCov-ln9CH4S_b_B3JfGbm0BMhCUS6D6Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am always having fun at this dentist. Everyone here is down-to-earth and lively. The hygienist Amy is so cheerful and knowledgeable. Dr. Cindy Tseng is helpful and intelligent. Just a good all-around vibes. I recommend this place to all my friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen Mistele","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_Wfmo4nRI8xXHZfHOWVpm6ncGeNZnePQU86JRqhti-dQK1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best dentist I’ve ever had! The staff makes the experience surprisingly enjoyable, and they are clearly experts in their field. They’ll even rate your teeth if you ask!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kimberly Dello Russo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZpUqSGZOmXmFl-35CafsWDmHm7kJdGb-KSSXTJWgoXqBy3gLP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After moving to Seattle two years ago, I had some trouble finding a great dentist. The search is over!  I am so thankful my coworker recommended Dr. Tseng’s office; my experience has been wonderful in every interaction. Clean office, knowledgeable staff, and I felt truly taken care of. HIGHLY RECOMMEND!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"LJ C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJQxFxhjFmR4QTlBQLgAr4ws8y32w4f4r-xxGp6J5xbbL7bA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't rave enough about the kindness and knowledgeable care you get at Cindy Tseng's office. Amy will make you not hate getting your teeth cleaned!  She's really good and tells you in the nicest way when you need to do better at flossing.  Everyone in the office is friendly and helpful. I've been seeing them for five years now and couldn't be happier.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOqYIeEKhObPdUjLbBGieGHtVjx5z5yQSgdZYL7EzuRxKlpxrl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I straight up hate going to the dentist - I never get any good news no matter how much at home care I do. What I like about Dr. Tseng is she is upfront about what you need that's concerning her and what can wait. This is especially helpful information when your insurance can only cover so much in a calendar year.\n\nShe and her staff (Amy was my hygienist, mad props to her) are friendly, welcoming, and non-judgmental. If you have to go to the dentist (and you should), go here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Raridan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUugrL2CPx0QLPf7TuX7MljnmSxCrS8HK7HASIpqFT05enJJMvHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been seeing Dr. Cindy for nearly 5 years. Originally,  I chose this office due to the proximity to my workplace, but even after changing jobs and no longer working downtown, it is still completely worth it to me to make special trips to continue to see Dr. Cindy and her amazing staff (special shout out to Linsey!) Visits are efficient but still very friendly and I receive a lot of reminders leading up to the appointment, which I appreciate. I look forward to my twice a year exams 😁 I highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
