ebit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"kaka jia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXG5-rlg3jzoQW1kTFjoFrSUOBBLMxOPRuUpBv7qnBRWSagQ14=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had wonderful experience with Dr. Ciao and his hygienist. Very gentle, thorough, and most of all genuinely caring. We had some bad news which is that some of my old root canals have to go because they are infected, but good news is we found the source of my chronic illness and I am looking forward to regaining my health under Dr. Ciao’s care. I waited several weeks to see Biological Dentistry and it’s definitely worth the wait.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harrison Carrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc0EaYIavpFYoXoOqOMOzqcMogqdHxKmS5yoXm7ZjjfFtwpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Because of my multiple chemical sensitivities, I stayed away from the dentist for years. This was the first place where I felt comfortable. The welcoming staff, calm music, and even their warm tea made a difference in my first visit which helped me feel confident in the following appointments. They removed an infected tooth that had been impacting my health, cleared out a significant infection, and eventually placed a ceramic implant that my body accepted smoothly. It's hard to believe that I went through these treatments without needing to be put under sleep.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yibo Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtzYe4-mgr2hlLNWGM_cxMqpVpEVPYHKJD0ZIWJy0qalvMjPIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been with Dr. Cziao and his team for many years now. They’ve been always caring and professional. When my veneer broke in half, I was under extreme stress from the sensitivity and a public appearance within few days. As always, they got all my information ready, got me in and did a treatment on the same day. My new veneers came out very natural and seamless. Definitely owe this guys a big award!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shane Wallace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPzTE_dCIjmbpRZVSgtiemYpgCxLlHdnaR-lY3CdcIiJDcgg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Calm, professional, patient centered office. I remember on my first visit, I waited 2 months to get in, but now to think of it, I feel blessed to have found Dr. C. I was dealing with severe gum disease and all the dentists I’ve seen, can only tell me to brush and floss better and get gum graft. This game plan changed completely when I met with Dr. C. He and his hygienist did a biological deep cleaning combined with laser and within 6 weeks, I saw improvement. 🙏🙏🙏.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzw_c3xS2-xGe1VAPztkaByNwJW6gFtxUDzYKmZIP94WzPZwM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone is very professional, highly knowledgeable, and kind. They don’t contract with my insurance but saves me a lot of work by filing to my insurance. Most of all, definitely appreciate the authentic biological perspective to oral care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zhiqi Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOcVC3IaE4ldlajIsR5vJQZ5ybS4NsH5Lx39NNmT0c3KKCvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve struggled with gum disease for years and kept needing deep cleanings every couple years on top of my routine cleaning every 3 months. My gut told me there had to be a better way. After meeting Dr. Cziao, he explained how bacteria affect overall health and suggested starting with a routine cleaning and laser therapy. His hygienist checked my mouth biome and saliva pH, then gave me a home protocol to follow until my next appointment. Ten weeks later, my gums improved and started looking healthier without the need of another deep cleaning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Moore Amanda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLp3vbo_xAamOLgr7Y8vUbxw8rxAAHF9xyXgG8hGf4qrCpsuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dental clinic is truly professional! The dentist is patient and detail-oriented, and the whole check-up and treatment made me feel very comfortable. The place is clean and welcoming, and the staff are super friendly. Overall, a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randy Steward","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKR-0wX9lD3Jg3SjeV0yI1Z6QoCEPl8bI0DyJjcZyhxOZCFFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As someone living with Hashimoto’s, I’m very cautious about anything that is introduced to my body, especially my mouth. As soon as I discovered that there are toxins inside dental materials (possibly inside my mouth), I began my search for a good biological dentist. Seattle Dental Care understood my concerns right away and went over how to safely remove mercury fillings from my mouth and replace them with something that my body can handle.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
