abled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Mirielle Encarnacion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtruHV2j9z9udyITyVovzFkG4ly0dYPMgd-seY6_oVlvrEQWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always have a great experience at this dental office. The entire team is friendly, welcoming, and very accommodating. My dental hygienist, Crissa, is incredibly thorough and makes every visit comfortable and pleasant. Dr. Bridget Singh is professional, knowledgeable, and takes the time to explain everything clearly. I highly recommend this practice and look forward to continuing my care here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Barron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVp3qL67n3v0xZb3X2wtfGcFfp67VJPgj_Kr1tTLkt9kkvKB1kS3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a great experience at this office for my dental cleaning. My hygienist, Carissa, was absolutely amazing. She was gentle, thorough, and made me feel completely comfortable the entire time. She explained everything she was doing and was very attentive to my comfort, which I really appreciated. My teeth felt incredibly clean afterward, and the whole visit was smooth and positive. Highly recommend this office  and especially Carissa.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ian Stanchi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW4OkJs40Pfa-s_6i-OkzXqkFTO0RJzvqjAEibOdCzODvIoAdd7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dentist office is great! Been coming here since 2021. Staff are super friendly and professional. Their cleaning rooms are comfortable and they have TVs and will put on Netflix if you want. I'd never seen that before. They're great to text appointment reminders and are always flexible to change and will even call if there's an opportunity to come earlier. Parking is tricky but I just park at Amazon garages and walk over (Doppler has two hours guest parking and very close). All around very happy and would recommend this office to anyone looking for a dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Florian Schiffers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFXh41kXkQ3UKi3dIRtox9W0UKIBN4_GbgKsg6C64FXJUz0pM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First dentist experience in the US and it's been great overall. Scheduling via zocdoc was efficient, the team reached out before and asked great initial questions. I came early and had everything done super quick. Assistants are super nice as well as Dr. Singh. Equipment is top notch and modern. Great communication and great proposed treatment plan. 100% will come here again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cassady Garner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAwSQRWlyXpXTEu0YbrGT-fpM19A7JgJySbJAdjt-xS6Gfzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you want to find sunshine in Seattle go to Dr Bridget Singh office and see Crissa. She made it feel like a spa day. Dr Bridget Singh is a great dentist. I look forward going back to the dentist because of the team here. They all work together to make you feel comfortable and taken care of. I’m really grateful to have found this office. Shahbano wad quick to respond and very kind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vibhav Kamat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCo_agWAfYtxvTFXR9zQG76EtLviZC1mJJVBjrS5HmzagH2_oN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve always been genuinely scared of going to the dentist, but my experience here changed that. From the moment I walked in, the entire team was warm, welcoming, and incredibly attentive. Dr. Singh is super friendly, approachable, and takes the time to make sure you feel comfortable and at ease.\n\nThe team truly goes above and beyond to ensure patient comfort, which makes a world of difference, especially if you’re someone who feels anxious about dental visits.\n\nA special shoutout and huge kudos to Crissa, who was absolutely exceptional. Her approach, patience, and skill were outstanding. I honestly did not feel pain even for a moment during my teeth cleaning, which is something I never thought I’d say about a dental appointment.\n\nHighly recommend this practice to anyone, especially if you’ve been nervous or hesitant about seeing a dentist. You’ll be in very good hands here. Easy reminders and alerts are always helpful, they even helped connect with Dental Surgeon and Endodentist for my condition.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morgan Atkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQvi4bDHM2lX52_WyVQj9dl0lXm6YPKG4La4UZKNhaX21c-DBlqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great, helpful, passionate staff! I learned helpful information to help me take care of my teeth/mouth. I hadn’t been to the dentist in awhile and they made me feel comfortable. Flexible appointment options too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paarthvi Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9mjTRQOuKJgoJ7OmvuiZ6LYxHqg4sxsIjv7e8vkgN-gsI1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great clinic, has amazing staff. The team goes above and beyond to ensure patient comfort. I did my Invisalign procedure with them and it was pretty smooth. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
