edit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Perrin lafky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU11PZscRTtEkNKAfxoa0sEzkUKowlcmHXAVtAXMap6OmlAJg_6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I truly cannot recommend this practice enough. I recently moved across the country and make sure to schedule my appointments for when I’m in town because Dr. Brenner is by far the best dentist I’ve ever been to. Everyone who works here is warm, friendly, and goes above and beyond to make their patients relaxed and comfortable. I am pretty anxious about dentist appointments, and on my first visit they took the time to understand how to make my experience as easy for me as possible. I also really appreciate that I’ve never felt pressured in any care decisions, and have always been given several options to choose from.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Iverson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaWg6yz6-jqTewdBko17AbHS5PZ3cm0Zmu_z7arzuRxLe6UXxe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Brenner Dental Care for many years and they have been one of the only dentist offices that have taken me seriously. Their level of attention to details and empathy is unmatched to anywhere else. I fully trust Dr. Brenner and highly recommend his office to anyone who has concerns or fears around dentists.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sheri sweeney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfQ9QsLbOqDlkyVAM16Woem9F6AE1NQAG6A3s_VNnDXOJ-bv8AEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Brenner and the staff are amazing. There is nothing too challenging for him to correct. I was in a very bad auto accident with three porcelain crowns knock out of my mouth. I now have TMJ for the first time in my life. Dr. Brenner and staff are able to diagnose treatment and navigate my care to restored smile and treat the painful TMJ.\n\nThey are understanding, professional,  knowledgeable  and very compassionate about dentistry.\n\nThank you Dr. Brenner and staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cindy Liao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7udvo03OHgXvgmVByWAXZNNQh_JiSgJ33syeFYfH47wGJCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best experiences I’ve had at the dentist. Every staff member, from the moment I walked in, was friendly and helpful. The patient intake felt comprehensive and Cindy did a great job cleaning my teeth I was comfortable the whole time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Jensen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEMfw_38HWpTBg7_suyMdUukjunNgDM0BUTSw4y5n4FyUsMGU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very honest and gentle group. Highly professional staff. Dr. Brenner identifies available options and doesn’t shy away from talking about the value proposition of certain procedures compared to others while  providing good well informed advice. Unlike many I’ve experienced in Seattle, he  seems to focus on overall patient care more than closing the sale on multiple procedures.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diane McCullough","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkLES0aOyyUJ_sbHuTEB-MLaK4H1vp-j5ef563E_JTUUrDZHk7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a cleaning scheduled; the night before I popped one of my crowns. Not only got my appointment taken care of, but Dr. Brenner was also able to get my crown put back on, saving me from an additional appointment. Thanks to Dr. Brenner and his staff for accommodating me on short, short notice!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Val Carrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOwGqFh6Y9KIGJ8MpLE4KdyVG6qyr8eiu_N5hyTnSAolhMPRE4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has been a real pleasure to visit Dr Brenner's office. They have done all my dental preventative care and some more for the last five years without any issues. The entire staff is extremely friendly and knowledgeable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1CnQpeitJu7WiDtjYFXWy2_k59Xvfssj9d6ea6MoZG5skqcsk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've had a few dentists over the years, and Dr. Brenner is by far the best. His office is equipped with advanced technology, and his staff is friendly and professional. I don't dread the visits as much as you'd expect—especially considering they're dental appointments! The hygienists are also excellent.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
