bility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible seating","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Colo Coolin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeuI3akwziTN3Hr839h3ModKN5wRiwGCA6y0gDpO9CLVE5U6E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I paid over $400 to have a broken tooth removed, and I left the doctor’s office in unbearable pain. I was not prescribed any pain medication, and now, almost a week later, I am still suffering from pain after a procedure that involved removing just one tooth 💔.\n\nDr. Atwood showed no care or concern for my well-being. As a person of color, I truly felt dismissed and unheard. No patient should ever be treated this way, especially when they are in pain and trusting a doctor for help.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0X2nHTmMyUMD-2iazc6BQcxiN8xe9A41IAAcDUkvNdLv6cQEQCuaGsYn93y0wq-UprYdcw0MO1ZlnHVl8EiR141LpZQ1WYE2qLD9hqV4vfLBjrWrfLCzTFOgxNpfVYfT8hnyJtBOT5vq9p=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2rS116o3zffhw-rIuA-8hc5sD14EmsK3akiW5HvW9Ar6QVod6DqIFKvJGFoI179sKbxTCRyWD91_4G84VeLfjwHqEmpap7F2NEq6PE-nwhWQ2IdyXgZCfmkJzmmhjePVAkInZfawpoqomB=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-5"},{"Name":"Palmo Corbus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHILd1rdrgtctJA0TerWXWdqx1Vw69MC1-aEJbVHg-FLo2fw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Corporate decisions on staffing is horrible. Staff onsite are extremely kind, helpful, and, professional, but COMPLETELY criminally understaffed. Only one dentist and one assistant. The dental assistant had to leave mid-procedure for a lunch break (legally mandated timing). The single dentist was hopping between patents trying to handle everyone (three rooms). He did a great job, but it both took forever, and, probably could have been better work if he had less to focus on. And if he didn't have to do two people's job for a while. Corporate needs to step up.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Jewell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlJ6tbO8BRme1o_N3WWV0nHqhXPK96b8rlWo9CNjmU81hcZ29BAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely phenomenal place to trust you’ll get quality and empathetic service. I don’t have dental insurance right now but definitely didn’t mind paying the cost since the Dentist was personable and cared  about my treatment. I was a human in her chair, not just a number. I wish I lived here so I could keep a dentist like her! The staff were equally as gentle and patient as well. All around great place for dental services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicholas Ferland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXp6aPR7Z2inDf2_RzfX4cfLCBpHfZQ-w2cxCOXSrXGibwxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Staff are nice, dentist was nice and understanding. Now it is my fault I neglected my teeth.\n\nBut this place felt like a bait and switch. Did the comprehensive exam, my insurance cover's one per year. Found several problems, got quoted 9000 plus to fix it. But they office only does insurance plans through affirm or sunbit. They do not just allow payments plans directly through their office.\n\nWhen I got home called the UW school of dentistry and another dentist a friend recommended in Northgate. They both can do the service. Both of them WILL accept payments plans directly through their clinic and not force you to use a credit company. But now I need to wait till the new year because this company used my one comprehensive exam for the year. $50 and an hour or so wasted. If you have a dental emergency I'd just go through a local ER and ask to see their on staff oral surgeon at this point. At that point at least you'd be able to setup a hospital payment plan.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa Roe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw7mn8AeRDg7kJfyCCliZ6jwOXK1QOuXtumIqqWATKTCc8_yvXAg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've had two root canal. Everyone is exceptional at their jobs. They go out of their way to make sure you're comfortable. I recommend them","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Underwood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlXTIMypcXG1ZrlObPLzXtJE12f4QDSOSx55dwvNw412jVDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"⚠️ WARNING: DEAF DISCRIMINATION \u0026 INSURANCE EXPLOITATION ⚠️\n\nI went to this dental office desperate for dental care (infected tooth for 2 months). My insurance is IN NETWORK, confirmed by my agent the night before.\n\nWhen I arrived, the front desk staff claimed the office was not in network and demanded I pay full cost upfront. This was a lie, clearly prepared to exploit Deaf patients.\n\nThis office assumes Deaf patients don’t understand insurance and intentionally tries to take advantage.\n\nDO NOT GO HERE if you are Deaf or rely on insurance.\nThis behavior is unethical, discriminatory, and unacceptable. Protect yourself.\n\nPS: I am already prepared for the office’s response and I will make an update as soon as I get their response, especially if they attempt to defend themselves or avoid taking accountability for their behaviors.\n\nYour respose was a lie. I've verified with my insurance and they ARE IN NETWORK.\n\nI have proofs. Should I expose this out in public?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janelle Yoshimoto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZNHD4Vb2DqD4wb450fUgtOp6uoGhW-XnHie94ilugt-SOviw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I could not ask for a better experience with not knowing i had to get a wisdom tooth pulled to help alleviate the pain I was feeling. It started with a warm welcome of Elizabeth, who is the front desk administrator but she was so much more than that. She was delightful and informative and the dental assistant (so sorry i forgot your name) was a delight as well, I immediately felt comfortable walking in and going to the back where my appointment started. The oral surgeon and dentist Walter has this superpower of making you feel so comfortable even knowing I had to get a tooth pulled. What a great team this was and it was such a smooth process from beginning to end. I get nervous going into dental or doctor's appointments but this was alleviated by the team at Emergency Dental Care. Im so grateful them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"LaChina Acissej","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZrJg-KzElasA5D-5gj86NQ2EsSKLOU57qCKwP_msYPW8MXjU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The place is nice and clean, the receptionist at the desk Sara is super friendly and kind.\nSteven one of the assistance was rude and not welcoming, he seemed upset that he had to actually work ..? I asked him a question and he seemed pissed off, he asked “whose the one that I have to speak Spanish to?” like boy did you not see the name it’s a guys name, use your brain. I asked another question and he seemed pissed off, it’s not like he does a lot of work either. The doctor was nice and professional. I will not be coming back here though, almost spent $800 just for a tooth extraction.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3TAW__Ci911OtyEsVn4_Hfl-3a1gnSXNOXFGCngEwF9RKT22MWasq4C2POdq9aF20ZNO51HlnpOQ6bwBe_nRmuRv7JzKPjvw1MhorNFRYFRSz5-xj8kIlwu9i3Bf3DMMWVua9S=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-18"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
