"Becca Mercado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV17Yuk6rEs27IKigqr5W3tAPoop8D2kHztEOzzqBC0c2_SchKY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I wasn't going to leave a review and just cut my losses, but I still think about my experience to this day. I had a completely fine initial first appointment, but I was there over 3 hours.\n\nThe second time I went in for a cleaning, I had a very uncomfortable experience. The dental assistants were all very nice but during my cleaning, Dr. Sohn was very rude to one of the dental assistants. She kept telling her that what she was preparing was wrong, and it was a very uncomfortable conversation to be having with a patient in the room. At some point, I believe the assistant started to tear up from how mean Dr. Sohn was being to this assistant.\n\nNot only was this so uncomfortable to witness, I also felt really unsafe during my cleaning. One of the pumps wasn't filled with water. Apparently things weren't properly set up.\nDr. Sohn also speaks very quickly and all in terms that I had trouble understanding. It felt like they were trying to get me out as soon as possible, yet the process was still incredibly long. I get maybe 5 minutes with the actual doctor and the rest is just waiting and filler.\n\nI have not been back since my last appointment because I was so thrown off by the way she treated that poor dental assistant. I hope the dental assistants are being treated fairly.\n\nTwo stars because of the receptionist and one of the dental assistants there too. Awesome experience with the receptionist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony Webb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVd8yr-6O6wEVKN2l-1YvPeZRbhLHegY17Xmaa-cri0Q3sSFsZu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ms. Annie Sohn, DDS, PS, is very kind and professional, as is the whole team at Smile Esthetic. I felt at home. They are skilled,  friendly and compassionate, using modern high tech equipment. I was treated as a VIP.\nLots of Love!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1FKzaEuPZi-xiSilQLcEjvs4mdt-Ul9OTsaxXE9uF8Xz162aHlIQsmM3VxMg24ydaUJERgYbihJGl25XB_qIr7vVhM6YTYGvj4RRB1ps8LU6kbth4czek83HxWFVwpX-LgPQlS_8KzOsqu=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-5"},{"Name":"Nathan Griffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXzSoJOb9YGlhCEP4dPGakTkE7XB7jRQl49hAEERs8b8C-uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeremy is a great hygienist, very calm, thorough, and gentle. Dr. Sohn is very knowledgeable, efficient, and quick at her job. She makes sure to explain what's going on and check in with the patient to see if they are comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jasmine McKinney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6EYMZYXdUpuqdXiPFLacrKR7CXdQen38d_EDtSt5WoL1NbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love Dr. Sohn! She is freaking amazing! She is just the epitome of a Virgo. As someone who describes themselves as incredibly analytical, I’ve met my match. The absolute attention to detail! This woman has such state of the art equipment. Something that took weeks at my last office took a few hours here, and only because we used the time wisely, and I had other work done while my crown was being made. Also, this office works with Cherry. I applied for Cherry and was approved instantly and the process was so quick and painless! From applying to checking out today. Jeremy was fantastic, Kris is amazing! Moji was super friendly and helpful as well. Really love this office, and thrilled I found them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Francis Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWA7TgX99oxUusyQAFkJUYAWvghsGe_SPdjpJbH0bi2G28qrBju=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited for the first time for a regular checkup and hygiene, and it was easy to make an appointment. The front desk staff were very friendly, and the doctor provided a thorough examination and clearly explained how to take care of my teeth. I plan to continue visiting in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe2H5RZ_-_6yY6-EuM9VDS4tmUxZ34Gw6eaWVp3lqd81KP6VyM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My very first visit with Dr Sohn and it was great! She listened to and addressed all my concerns. Very professional! She made me feel very comfortable and well cared for. Great visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chato Pierides","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5ZiQzpyzy3PAhhZ4NhDZmGcYReS04g-1vEccgF7gaijbi4qof=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit with the dentist.  I wanted something done and discussed it with my doctor and she started and got prepared  to do the examination, took digital impressions for my dentures.  It went smoothly and I am satisfied and happy with the progress.  The staff were professional too.   Glad to have come to this dental appointment and of course, I will be happy to share this experience and recommend it to anyone that need dentures. Thank you","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Wilburn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqwS7pKdLGG_4k8DBeGk0NTtLRfC0syUVRXLh6A3do3K1KBYkB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"She was honest with me about my options and what steps I would have and go through to achieve my best result.  I appreciated that. She gave me consideration and resources to help me navigate the journey to wellness. Good doc.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
