omplete_address":{"borough":"Central Business District","street":"509 Olive Wy #1653","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98101","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jeannie Francis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYWAfr2iYeQdVZwvvcpSLoZusfprEbm5qO-osiFDKIqXHVxs9g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. Vo's for 20+ years. He and his staff are awesome! Nothing but professional always.\n\nOver the years Dr. Vo has personally helped me overcome my fear of dentists by providing gentle yet effective procedures. His gentle manner helps me relax and that helps me through the most involved procedures. I trust him completely.\n\nHe and his staff always put patients first.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob Rosner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcgtw3rbEwgPhqXtObdbrso5De8H3BgLYT8DZwOZroeC4kd1s5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Vo installed four crowns for me. I was prepared for a dentist, what I also got was an artist. He was very concerned about how my new teeth would look. He worked very closely with my oral surgeon to design how my teeth would fit into my mouth. He was professional, caring, creative and very talented. I would recommend him to anyone. Great work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandra Styles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1x6atBYbjLSCgVEK81imJVjPrMILYgb7ZIO4PXTW0WjSVgyh0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a fantastic experience at my favorite dental office, and I can't recommend it enough! My dental cleaning with Frank was exceptional. He was thorough and gentle, making sure I felt comfortable throughout the entire process. Frank's friendly demeanor put me at ease, and I left feeling refreshed and confident about my oral health.\n\nWhen it came time for my fillings with Dr. Jon, I was a bit nervous. However, Dr. Jon quickly alleviated my concerns with his calm and reassuring approach. He took the time to explain each step of the procedure, which helped me feel more relaxed. His assistant, Hailey, was equally amazing! She was attentive and supportive, making sure I was comfortable and informed during the entire process.\n\nTogether, they created a positive and caring environment that made my dental visit a breeze. I truly appreciate their professionalism and dedication to patient care. If you’re looking for a dental team that goes above and beyond, Frank, Dr. Jon, and Hailey are the ones to see! Thank you for making my dental experience so pleasant!\n\nP.S. I work in dental care also and this is the number one place I recommend to colleagues and other dental professionals. The absolute top of dental care is with Dr. Jon and his team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaimee V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL92eDMlUO5WRadDYkhHi5C5WUmGA5VtgII8p8RknIlIjdXuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Their customer service is terrible. One of the worst experiences I’ve ever had. I made sure everything was good before leaving the office and then all of a sudden they start harassing me and sending me bills for $60 and escalated it to collections. Get your money before you let people leave and inconvenience them. Atrocious.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"E L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgM061FQuqOVPdLeQtai2Sb6asfMGOp5qTu3mzCbXDldbArWc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Vo and his team have been so lovely to work with over the years, they have been very patient, diligent, and transparent. I would recommend them to anyone.\n\nAlso shout out to hygienist Jeff - he was very knowledgeable, patient with answering questions, and did an amazing thorough cleaning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiqH7OZcGZesG7kbOXAZFR38fXNp_Cc18qhtuvKh_m3K6Z3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had Dr. Vo for my dentist for over 10 years and I cannot say enough about him and his staff! He is a great dentist; he knows what he's doing, listens to his patients and is HONEST! He does not try to sell you on work you don't actually need; he will explain what's wrong and what the options are and let you decide. Also, his dental hygienists are very gentle! I'd highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"lisa huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCToXxuU37SKBJ7e5XZFYUULfTGrTtWJZuJiU88_4kLBVvlHE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Vo is a wonderful dentist- friendly, and professional. He takes extra care to put his patients at ease and checked on me several times during the visit (remove old filling, clean out cavity and refill). Dr. Vo explained each setup and made sure I was comfortable during the processed. Very efficient too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hyeyoung Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHh1FQSii25s5inuZlo3_CAF9GIaLGbX_0TM1LrxCDRDgcxn-gDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Its been 5 years with them, and this time it was also really pleasant to be there. The staffs were very kind and warm. There was an issue with my appointment, but they were able to fix it and I could see Dr.Vo even though he was busy. He is always super friendly. Overall I am satisfied with this clinic.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
