in the downtown Seattle area. She is thorough in her exam, takes time to listen and never suggests unnecessary procedures. The office and the staff are also very welcoming and helpful. We are so glad we found this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Isaac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFNs-5nRsS9lr2Wj0Q3nshAic0Bo1HojVkvfFd0s-9zev7Ojk4oA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Quaidoo and her team are beyond fantastic. Her office is clean, quiet, and their on-site equipment is state of the art (including a water-cooled CNC mill to produce color matched zirconia crystalline crowns on-site in minutes). Generally, I do not like going to the dentist. I hardly ever trust that am not being sold on something I don't need. Dr. Quaidoo is as honest as could be and she is a skilled doctor and technician. She and her team (dental assistant and receptionist) are exceedingly friendly, knowledgeable, effective, and accommodating. These were easily the best dentist visits I've ever experienced (and the only time my \"bite\" has felt the same after significant work, like it never happened).\n\nWhen I come back to Seattle, this is the only dentist I'll see. I might even fly back to Seattle for a dentist appointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Richter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViHD5Y3tq067R_GYabqIwbEH6YPKVSCRtjflcetxKZwaz21HGWnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands down the best experience I’ve ever had at the dentist. The entire staff was friendly and made great conversation with me! I found out my assistant and I were from the same country and the receptionist recommended me some dairy free options when I mentioned I was going dairy free. I had never been there before and the receptionist already knew who I was! The examination was thorough and you could tell the dentist really cared about making sure every box was checked. They gave me a detailed plan and made sure I was clued into the entire process. Could not recommend this place enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saket Sinha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-py_C-tYqLH4ZeFNrbux0n1cblsHw_1TBH5ZcAMrIXYs7KyLL_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been with Smile Matters and Dr Quaidoo for over 1.5 years. I have gone through several filing and am currently 6 months into my braces. I have seen exceptional care and wonderful customer service during my time here. I am not the most punctual patient and the clinic has been very accommodating to my schedule which is much appreciated. I would recommend this dental clinic to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ruthanne Romero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLonlQmFxLU87tm-KC62eMsPmwt7QEvCNjBSZbL-B8jup3ajf5u=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Q and her Staff are great! They are very friendly and professional, keep the office clean and tidy but welcoming, and seem to always be on schedule. They take great care of my teeth and don't ever pressure me to get random dental work/accessories like I hear some other dentists do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Claudine Mboligikpelani Nako","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFBQ7E-gdifforRlr7Nziu5iq_2_wDQT_4iiaON9VYzf-wxsHfrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Quaidoo is awesome!! I’ve had several traumatic dental experiences and am always nervous for a new provider but I could not be happier now. She is so great at her job in addition to being a warm and caring professional. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"local","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGjrWhJPUyKQe3Du9K7glmz9FcfXw-JV3mURycTRSy1GNvbhI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found Dr. Quaidoo in an emergency in January 2020 after ignoring my dental health for a number of years. I am so thankful that she has remained available and has helped me rehabilitate my teeth. I cannot recommend her office enough for the care and concern that provide. It's so nice to not have any pain in my jaw anymore and to not be afraid to show off my teeth when I smile.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
