w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=306.9605\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"114678036515042378601","name":"Ballard Orthodontics (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114678036515042378601"},"complete_address":{"borough":"West Woodland","street":"1400 NW Market St Suite 102","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98107","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as Asian-owned","enabled":true},{"name":"Identifies as women-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Shannon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0rYiA8Q3jIIvyn4687ZTZOFFyqZg2CzklT8kv6Oa9a9xZRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ballard Orthodontics has been the most wonderful experience for our family, and I can’t say enough great things about this office. From the very first visit, the attention to detail was far beyond anything I had seen at other practices. The orthodontists are true airway specialists, and it shows in the way they evaluate growth, breathing, and overall facial development, not just the teeth. That level of expertise gave me so much confidence in the care my kids received.\n\nOne of my favorite parts of treatment has been the Dental Monitoring app. The weekly scan reviews make everything incredibly efficient, and I loved being able to message directly with the doctor. It felt like we had constant support without needing frequent in office visits.\n\nThey also went out of their way to accommodate my son when he had a pokey wire. I called in a panic, and they saw him right away with so much kindness and patience.\n\nAnd I have to mention my 7 year old, who has sensory issues. I never imagined he would be able to wear Invisalign, but it worked beautifully for him. He loved that he could still eat everything he wanted, and the process was easy, comfortable, and stress free. I am truly grateful for Ballard Orthodontics!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn20tl7Vw8fmQaoJ7lRzWhU758qi3cD2idZ64VYupAZVNXuKgXCUncGbSW7uL6AMjXd7zBJJUHxS0uvsfmvhUzi4s34LjWYWOcByoyOn0C6mo4zhkihvpSwpNLYAAcWkskB-QWRuOBr7o0iB=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0HJdl89pt-m9LwJlOGieZwDizZMea-KhR-cYyqNQnbyAqYOYsrvWh7yIK41wDYn-BOFqXEuyjhBNGNxO3W3Hlof1y6_I3xYl1gDThbj81mlrBOLWeYj-CTvN_A7P9MKsrdC0LXy5fnl-yR=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0E24Dy7GQE19w08AIrGH8fSCEK_smHjzVHJs66fK5INdX2reteznVeWHdjtvGx1WL9KwNqYKraweNwnYsS-yI9bwJrPvjy62dHw_oQsEailtStmvW2zyhUpIiu7sZnmGtigHuOhS1IxX7a=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2R4ZOwynD0ghU0TjZU24CBgNpvK3NKQboxEmknavlUK9-4IrJBGzURQW3GarkuEHxlU4XNW8PxaIFGyu7egP4r-xkErI8stUaJIJF7BYIBjZqEu7DYpde6DfB1Kc0c89pHErQurqka0Gri=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-13"},{"Name":"Lexi S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqh7WqMWNwirY-Pv3RkIHtcxYylVMKsk3-r7d7o1ErNxiY49g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is absolutely wonderful! All the staff are incredibly friendly, helpful, and very knowledgeable. The doctors have mastered the art of ortho, and I can’t thank them enough for helping give me such a beautiful smile!\nThe clinic is clean, with updated technology that makes treatments more efficient, precise, and worry-free. The admin team is also very quick with responses, which makes scheduling and communication so easy.\nOverall…… it was a perfect experience. Thank you to the Ballard Ortho team! 🤩","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QnHPGqON8aJqf_DiSaNKkcOmRxDAvrkA8AK6umLG2WnPShp_kojDeQzrgRyGH9iBI48gNB4Or1JTw_lRjaH-KK0hbaaGFeQCb5xB16dBCvB9vJlgs3CcAWvm1Y76fj2aMziT4JHnZ05zX=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-5"},{"Name":"Linda Rabadi Fair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3Q2xs4EJFDc_8Yk_PuUWEgoNv85TvrU8SapOVPecVWTo54Ws=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loved our experience at Ballard ortho! We received exceptional and consistent care; the team always made my daughter comfortable (she was age 10-12 during our time with Ballard ortho.) We never received any surprise bills, the quote we received was the same amount we paid over 2 years later. Thanks Ballard Ortho!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lawrence Stevens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVl-q3p3OCqC0A4BdZyLwuMMziTpgcssks5Lhmj4NRU65JFL5YP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love Ballard Orthodontics and all of the wonderful, amazing women who work here. They are kind, transparent, and truly have you best interest at heart when it comes to your teeth. I got Invisalign and love the results so much! I couldn’t be happier and I’m so incredibly thankful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Soleman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1MShdeqRYcn78cA4yBb4XUltnXv-7oHeEEKL13sVveY81mIiww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are incredibly pleased with our experience at Ballard Orthodontics! Thanks to the state-of-the-art technology they significantly reduced the number of appointments. The staff is warm, friendly, and exceptionally professional. Dr. Shafeena Chatur is not only highly skilled but also genuinely attentive to our son’s needs. We are absolutely thrilled with the outcomes of his maxillary expansion and Invisalign treatment. We wholeheartedly recommend Ballard Orthodontics!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dante Martin Jr.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRIdNichM3f1wRLe0QWaWpGV2i4Rw0Gh18WOjeOVzyKxj9ZEEZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Five-star experience at Ballard Orthodontics! It was my first time in, and the team made it so easy. Lacey was so helpful and reassuring, Dr. Jan provided a very thorough consultation, and Lex finished things off with a quick scan. Professional, friendly, and efficient—I couldn’t have asked for a better visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanya Avoundjian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKc18NGFwwqzQYMLe7MruYytRq3cNuPBJIEGxrMBHrbpdkr-hMig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went in for a consultation at Ballard Orthodontics today, and it was so lovely! The staff is very friendly, welcoming, kind, and thorough. They walked me through the whole process of getting Invisalign from start to finish, and I left feeling confident and excited for my future smile. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Bell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbt_tHepYTk02vkFwMD0guo1bHtpHhNGJQx8DrMl5bYpLuKA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Beware of hidden costs not disclosed during consultation, like $1,000 additional fee for final Vivera retainers.\n\nI’d come out of a horrific experience with another ortho which I was very transparent about during my consultation, and they reassured me this experience would not exist here. A few days before I was about to pay and start my treatment I went with a friend to pick up her final retainers who was surprised when they were not the Vivera (Invisalign) retainers she’d been using her whole treatment. It was explained to her that these final retainers are made in house, and in order to get the Vivera retainers you need to pay an additional $1,000. I felt this was shady, so before paying for my treatment, I asked Lacey about this who confirmed this is in fact true. I expressed how this was quite misleading as the quote they give you upfront tells you final retainers are included as part of the package, but they do not state it’s retainers made in house that use a different cloudy material and that they are not fitted to your teeth with the scalloped edges (it’s just straight along your gums). As a grinder, this doesn’t work for me. Had I not asked this, they definitely were not about to mention it before I paid. This left me feeling like more surprises would arise if did decide to move forward with treatment through them. I called 2 of the other orthos I got quotes from and asked whether the final retainers were Vivera, and they both confirmed they were. I even contacted some friends in Canada who’d had Invisalign, and they also confirmed Vivera retainers were included in their treatment plan.\n\nOverall, the Ballard ortho team seems nice enough, and I did think their initial scan was the best compared to other orthos. That said, my advice is: do your research, ask the right questions, and if Vivera retainers are important to you - add $1,000 on top of your quote. There’s plenty of orthos here in Seattle, so I definitely recommend getting lots of quotes and evaluating!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
