u0026yaw=275.20578\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102291435877376746159","name":"Revive Smiles Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102291435877376746159"},"complete_address":{"borough":"South Lake Union","street":"259 Yale Ave N","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98109","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as Asian-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Paid parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Phil Flickinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpJfEHc4J4U4TDF4D5jI9nzbktpTAtURxm6aii_dFrsUgKwmhO-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I first discovered Dr. Bill Wong and his team back in 2011 when I first moved to Seattle. Over the next 18 months, they handled everything for me—from routine cleanings and whitening to an emergency chipped crown and some complex cosmetic work. When I moved to San Francisco for my job, I was bummed to leave this practice behind; I'd been in excellent hands, and the bar was set very high for my next dentist in California.\n\nFast forward 12 years: I moved back to Seattle and one of the first things I did was look up Dr. Bill. I was thrilled to find his new practice, Revive Smiles, a short walk from the heart of downtown where I work.\n\nHere is why I won’t go anywhere else:\n\nUnmatched Skill: Whether it’s fixing a cavity or identifying my teeth-grinding issues (and fitting me for a perfect mouthguard), his attention to detail is commendable. My teeth feel new after cleanings, and when he's fixed problems, they've been fixed for good.\n\nState-of-the-Art Tech: The office is modern and uses the latest equipment. I was most impressed by the 3D imaging tool they have. Bill made a detailed map of my teeth, and took me through a thorough plan to take care of them over the long term.\n\nReasonable \u0026 Seamless Rates: Revive Smiles' rates feel right; they've always worked hard to maximize my insurance, and when I've had to pay out of pocket for anything, the damage is minimal.\n\nA Personal Touch: Dr. Bill is a genuinely humble, kind person who gives back through volunteer work. That integrity shows in how he runs his practice.\n\nMy wife has also joined as a patient and is just as happy as I am. If you are looking for a dentist you can trust for the long haul, do yourself a favor and book at Revive Smiles. You won't regret it.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0OK-Zi1StMndt3ffB25vOfuVIpbhu8XN1eo8NniL2e_OOCAOMqvbpnnd6idXS0OwYFTWPrtdM7FsTX6INu600Xi3OMHONh8pUYw9aPwowvsVbzmUWNTr7qLNy1YC4tsXDJhN2FdHsKbqU=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-12"},{"Name":"Rebecca Duthie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYOBSTzXtBw0YBPfcG2rAn-YT-UEgLvh9b7i6p9--YQQ86fA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at Revive Smiles Dentistry are amazing!!! Everyone I have had interaction with are compassionate, professional and approachable.    Dr. Wong is a national treasure!   He is so compassionate and has a warm demeanor that puts you at ease! I feel very confident that I am receiving the highest level of care with Dr Wong and the rest of the Revive Smiles Team.  I consider myself very lucky to have the team as my dental care professionals.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Schneidler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9AOXAPYEYup2nLl1aKc4xZwupIkkuQcptPSRzZs9K5M9c1Lnr2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Bill and his team at Revive Smiles are almost too good to be true… but they ARE true.\n\nIt’s hard to write an adequate review of Dr Bill because if we were to write the truth, nobody would believe it. But I’m going to try and I give my word: this is all 100% true without exaggeration or hyperbole.\n\nMy family of 5 has been seeing Dr Bill for over 15 years. When we first started, it was after the 2007 market crash and I suddenly found myself the sole provider for our family and making only 40% of my normal pay and without benefits and no way to pay for dental coverage for my wife and I and our 3 young kids.\nWhen Bill heard about this, he scheduled for me and my family to come into his office during off hours when the regular office was closed just so he could provide dentistry for my family and he didn’t charge a thing. He didn’t do this just once or twice. He did it for more than a year until I was able to get back on my feet and get good dental insurance again.\n\nAnd it’s not just my family. I know first hand of several other families that have gone to Bill when they lacked insurance or the funds to fully pay and he took care of him.\n\nBill is an incredibly kind, genuine man. He’s the kind of person you would trust with your kids’ lives. When he says “I will take care of them for you. You don’t have to worry” you know he means it and I cannot adequately describe how that makes a parent feel.\n\nNowadays, we have full dental insurance and are able to pay. Bill has since moved his practice into Seattle and is much further away from where we live. But still, we drive 2x as far and pay bridge tolls and parking just so Bill can still be our dentist.\n\nI honestly can’t fully describe Bill’s kindness, but if you are still reading this and you are looking for a dentist and you live anywhere in the greater Seattle/Puget Sound area, you owe it to yourself and your loved ones to visit Bill Wong and his team at Revive Smiles. (Tell him Andrew S sent you and says “hi” 😊) You will be glad you did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aziz Shittu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUh4NabB-1kwjB5APyMdLq96XtcXbwJ26vlXv8Kz2cjisZ1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an opportunity to get an appointment for an exam of my teeth with Revive Smiles Dentistry, and it was really nice. Dr. Wong is a nice and warm person that always tried to give customer the best of the quality service to satisfy his customers. The service was great and the people there were welcoming and profesional.\nThank you again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diego Rivera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe84Wrxy78-ws1w0A-TqaQEEBRj4BSvifiR8cAU-VU2yEdbO8mMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a crown done by Dr. Bill at Revive Smiles Dentistry, and I couldn’t be more pleased with the experience.  He’s so calm and zen.  From start to finish, the team was professional, friendly, and highly skilled. Dr. Bill took the time to explain the procedure, ensuring I was comfortable and informed.\n\nThe fit and appearance of the crown was perfect, natural looking and comfortable from day one. The entire process was smooth, pain-free, and completed with great attention to detail. I truly appreciate their expertise and care, and I highly recommend Dr. Bill.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryce Christopher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNbAfC207L4tE0Orn_sQzGeT889bSX6NcgmBdkCQTbLu8t8g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very grateful for Dr. Wong and staff. They created a care plan that prioritized my immediate needs, and their follow through has been excellent. Dr. Wong displays unmatched expertise and professionalism, explains procedures in a way that makes sense, and most importantly, he sees the person in the chair behind the teeth, and wants to help them. My quality of life has improved since I have been under their care, and I look forward to continuing to accomplish my dental goals with them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prianca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLoPmGfeKKyYbn7tnhgbbX1j1ugsayCiT4SkwXVBXFa5vJAg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a welcoming experience. I’m not a fan of going to dentists but this visit has really warmed up my experience with dental care. Dr. Bill has such a great approach to making his patients feel welcomed and talking through every step. He was very genuine and informative. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Tiffany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4tI2dICgVXJyrMYso9tGwg87iefTVwpo7-aP3bbaYjFUJB5iy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love getting my teeth cleaned and maintained by Dr. Bill at Revive Smiles. I’ve been coming here for a over a year now. Dr. Bill is meticulous and provide gentle care for my teeth. Unlike my previous dentist who was the complete opposite, where everytime I would bleed after visits and one time accidentally took my chipped front tooth filling that I’d had for 10+years off. I then went to Dr. Bill ti fix my chipped front tooth and the process went very smoothly. Never had any pain during any of my visits. They also gave me a free teeth whitening tray to try out. Overall, great service and care. 10/10!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
