ing. The team is fantastic, the space is beautiful, and the care is excellent. Couldn’t recommend them more.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tara Davenport","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4aLIbWcrkzCX9ZouHv71Wg-Z42Hs0yZNpiBXuRWwjWbk_NrnHVw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seriously the nicest team — I was nervous because I don’t like going to the dentist and hadn’t in a long time, but they made me feel really comfortable. Felt like they were really thorough and they explained everything they were doing, but they didn’t push any unnecessary procedures or costs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie LeeKeenan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfebJQ8JZdY3pa8Xd-J27izEfW-qe_XlB7D1x4f8W07fq9Z5br=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Again a wonderful experience with Dr. Dubey and her team. I needed a new crown and she and her team handles my anxiety around dental work with reassurance and patiently answers any questions or concerns! Highly recommend! And they made the new crown in their office in 2 days!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyle H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfnmiNUSi2mAgt5UraVdb85fMCBw5CaSYEdHzzSS7X6AvJTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely professional from A to Z! Makes one fell very well cared for and always intersted in all aspects of thr process including such as walking one throught cost and options on charges in next stage scenario's. Much appreciated!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Berri Reifert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMg7SEohHJrQ_AM_Q7yV6neAzE-PxtX1v5Rr5dNd7LCfsPnsM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Supertooth is always kind, caring, thorough, and efficient. I’ve been going to there for 5+ years and have always had a good experience. The team has continuously gotten ahead of any dental issues I have before they became too problematic.","Images":["https