},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Strietzel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuVGLZtNRgLXT-7znSJMrIpQcOYWJ6rnxwMpNBiYJknIoI8FA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going to Simply Dental for 10 years now. It’s mostly only been for cleanings, but they also handled my wisdom teeth removal. I appreciate how straight forward and friendly they have been. I also never feel like they are trying to upsell me on something.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maggie Sean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaROi34J-jjucN3NadgpONa5mByTld4aykhqF4aHW8jwrd9tqq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really enjoy all the dentists and staff at this office. They are kind and genuine and offer personalized care. I don’t feel rushed during routine cleanings and they do great cleanings. A great neighborhood dentist. Really glad I found them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Tsang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVUEiV8WdkfWYuVv0FMeOfaTZqM84dtrrXtpq2fj6DqQZ2qiO8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I actually enjoy my dentist visits ever since I started visiting Simply Dental. My hygienist today was so personable and professional. She also took great care and did an amazing job restoring my smile. Very happy!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Y Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWaMUHCKHt_E4QE9_YdHbnSWcE8QlH8S4gjAfxbRc3DRow10-K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was an extremely unprofessional and disorganized experience.\n\nI had a root canal appointment scheduled for 11:30 AM, However, by 12:30 PM, I still had not started the treatment. The staff were constantly looking for tools and materials, seemingly not knowing where anything was located.\n\nThe dentist treated multiple patients at the same time and was very difficult to find throughout the process.\n\nAt one point, an assistant even asked me if I was another patient’s name, which was not me. That moment genuinely scared me, as it raised serious concerns about the possibility of treating the wrong tooth.\n\nOverall, the entire visit consisted of waiting for people, waiting for equipment, and watching staff search for things. This level of chaos does not inspire any confidence as a patient.\n\nI originally scheduled 3 treatment sessions, but after attending just one, I have decided to switch to another dental clinic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Walsh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuTRpC8VJDb9oYGtpcBcdIo0-1fRWwWTVDpTXTWPZj60PLgPkU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a fiercely loyal patient here for fifteen(?) years now. I left Seattle for a couple of years and never took the time to see a dentist while I was away. When I learned I'd be moving back to Seattle, *literally* the first call I made was to Simply Dental to book an appointment when I got back in town. True story. And  I've still never had a cavity fwiw.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ludfjig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCo_fj4Bkj7B9D7jxivWL8CBQOTHPkrZ3viWTT3VizSTsz1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was shocked to receive an unexpected $300 charge at checkout for a scan that no one mentioned to me beforehand. When I arrived for my appointment, they simply called my name, directed me to a machine, and performed the scan without explaining anything or telling me there would be an extra fee. This feels very misleading and unprofessional. I don’t think it’s normal to add such a charge without informing the patient first.\n\nEdit: I am happy with the resolution provided, changing to 4 starts instead","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melina Ward","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiE0auxuV962FVZ7eZgxb_Fp0APoQ13QcgrR-c1wWDA_5FxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Earlier today I visited the clinic for a routine cleaning and was impressed by how professional and friendly the staff were... Who else manages to keep the waiting room calm and the paperwork smooth while still making you feel at ease? I left feeling confident about my dental health and will definitely be back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yuan Tian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl670zpn6639IJG9v4mT6jGUVqs6hu1CyUN7bMAHkbdGFkyFs3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Don’t choose this clinic, especially if you are working under tech company and maybe trying to find a clinic which is nearby. They don’t have good communication with the customer. I got the email to pay the amount or call them. However the only button in the email is to give the credit card number. They don’t have the explanation where’s the amount coming from. You need to call them and verify if it’s a fair paid. They will also complain that it’s your insurance company issue.\nChoose here if you want to be bothered every payment","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
