atient here for years, and I cannot recommend them highly enough. The entire staff is incredibly personable, and the treatments are thorough and done with great care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Trey Littell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxu9UH5g9EFvEsVMkFKN31Z2S9fs4tauwVprY7JxVrIBN_WIWcAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a 5 star dentist. Do your teeth a favor. Go to this dentist! They are knowledgeable, experienced, talented, and passionate about your teeth. They did everything for way less than other dentists quoted me. Their customer service, capabilities, and overall treatment of their customers is world class. I have never gotten such pain free cost effective work done anywhere. This dental practice has such a wonderful team. I couldn’t be happier, and my teeth couldn’t look better. If this isn’t your first choice for dental work in Seattle, you are risking it. Go here and be confident that you will be treated right and not get overcharged.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0AefJvtq1yA2wl1EX1PyZYOqUsIFmYiGc5IAWSHvV5vFLNTQp7cHdJZed7JONWDw2Jellkg9p2Z_ISW6QeBJ-pz3CTPvF4XDrkDCINo2AHaSHv3aLZ5mjE8QtAsElQgfnl6pfylw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17y7wwiqZNNw-MCoHJuC8yPCIoBL8wUjfXa2cjVLOqwRIS9T4CaPlLIUrXCJJR6N4F-lmUAN0PK_6iQrDckId87CEtMLRDrUAft1YtQbgZW39Nmr7-uT6RCNpUBNM6Dx1vVVA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3pJCDSKj7JKxi-TwaO1Dzhm5wpHYg1IcS5GdlzrZQHB94_KwqqEKlcfLuEJrpYscGiPNpDMqD6d-sI4jX9r5JTTFLI2Gafv41wOoH7ssYrv3E9HgQUWm3IFwPi-zjVKaIzAIdE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3T4gAbPQD7J_vH6mV20rMNNyhqmjC0IEM2DIMHgiSEgQFHVszR2RgqZ6uxt0aMJ3O1y5H5qya4O4-UAVO0eRDJ5u17eC-LUDLFU4aXBXpSn8qv-YNQoPEMAqym70i5q7hSqg3O=k-no"],"When":"2019-5-24"},{"Name":"Scott Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHsPpjU-baqLxn3H0MXFU7XwE2Tp9_alKG9Hu2-9KS-8YzXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The entire team is great! I was treated very well and given honest feedback bout my oral health and treatment plan. Truly appreciate the staff and the experience. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"karen donald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIaq9RbGNJeGBaXg5WTdWKijViEYy0M9JtrUgnIqbSAte9iA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend coming here. I am 71 and I find that Seattle Downtown Dentist is the consistently the best dental experience that I’ve ever had. I actually don’t mind going to the dentist now because of the excellent care I get from the minute I walk in the door. Everyone who works there is very efficient and kind and my teeth are doing great. You won’t be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shruti Agrawal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRsBTjf6bnPo6XLBwz6d2WH-UhTHE4QKVLCgvpuPGmxgUq2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient with them for some time now and have always received the best care. The staff is attentive and responsive. I am not a fan of getting dental work done but the doctor made me feel very comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
