":[{"Name":"erica edwards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWef8tEITWzz2FHG-gMOdRhuTzv0oumTaI9YZgL9St0TGIVynb3IQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Dr. Azary! Not only is Dr. Azary amazing at dentistry, she is compassionate and kind!\nWhen you walk in and are greeted by Oriannys (Patient care coordinator (\nOr seated by Erin ( dental assistant) . Then meet Dr. Azary. You will have a sense of belonging from the whole team!  Thats exactly what they are, a team! They work so well together! My experience from the front door to leaving was flawless! I highly reccomend Dr. Azary and her wonderful team!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ishmeet Kohli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnzmwfxuXP5gR2FSkkRMEIjIrw8-yw2zUVgoyJJOF7Alz_SrlK6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely visit meeting with dr Armina Azary. They were very professional, and knowledgeable. Dr Azary kndly offered to try using my old crown rather than billing me for a brand new one right away. My first visit but I was very impressed and certain that they will be our new family dentist. I am glad to have found dr Azary for my tooth troubles.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lori Dinnison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqczpwsn0EKaQhUDs6R8fOulXmAr_CdSjkKK9Xomdwutl8kA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Raval and his team are wonderful.  I had a challenging issue which could have caused me to lose my front tooth due to root damage and bone loss.  Dr Raval took the time to consider options that could best maintain my tooth, and also helped to improve the condition of my bone structure going forward.  They were also very understanding about my dental anxiety and made the entire process very comfortable.  I’m very pleased with the outcome and would highly recommend Dr Raval.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"randy boe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHEwVqhDs7guf6hqOjLhWk4_eGvVhWqMpEI61I1I3zbg5jDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and Dr. Wong are all professional and very competent. Everyone there was extremely polite and they made my experience there while I was getting my tooth extracted a good one. I was very nervous despite having many teeth worked on in the past, and the Doctor and his assistant made my time in the chair a very positive experience. I highly recommend Revive Dentistry for all your Dental needs. 😃👍.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Richman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZwY6ZNnhGpA4403jj3GXHB5kOgA8DI3kIGyUVxcFjGHHxz87N=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff was very professional and friendly during my new patient visit.  The dentist (Armina) and the hygienist were very thorough in their exams and provided clear explanations. I highly recommend Love Your Smile!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Takis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5amWqBbOL-aNXWhSiS2_1OVRcmlxk17uQ6CSiAFQFA_AxoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today I went in and saw Dr. Raval for a follow up after my crown lengthening procedure. Dr. Raval is really kind and helpful, he answered any questions my daughter and I had. It is healed amazingly and I was able to schedule for my crown👑. I am always so thankful for everyone here at this wonderful establishment. Thank you Love Your Smile!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rosmalys Campero La Rosa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRCuE_vP-neEdYnQoEn8pbLHTv5AqZUfw1wbe4x95O2EWI-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Team at this clinic is fantastic, they all are very friendly and attentive with patients. Doctor Armina did a great cleaning and Ori was well understood my concerns and what I wanted to get done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNIX5F