s":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://seattlewadentistry.com/book-an-appointment/","source":"seattlewadentistry.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"107048856835908683074","name":"Capitol Hill Seattle Dentist (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107048856835908683074"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Pike/Pine","street":"963 E Union St","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98122","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"keto3000","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVydWR1zhG0llJHnRmY7dNGmXoHuat3qqKFSI6C5YSgltDllQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had many dentists in life, some good some not-so-much. Dr Kim is by far one of my all-time favorites!  Whether it’s fillings, crowns, gum issues or just my regular checkups \u0026 cleanings, I actually enjoy \u0026 look forward to my visits since I know I will get the best dental care possible!\nDr. Kim is highly professional, gentle, thorough and always has a smile with her patients.\nAll her staff- hygienists, admin, etc are well trained, cheerful. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raymond Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe7ZECvgVVePiu9VVPfmGlCmsFirw6GMSJ_oNCTJ5YJEWq5RQV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I appreciate how Seattle's Capitol Hill Dentist combines professionalism with a personal touch. They remember details about your life, follow up on concerns from previous visits, and make you feel like more than just another patient. My insurance expires this month and they spared no expense in getting me booked in ASAP. I had doctor Kim as my doctor and Jenn as my hygienist. Super super friendly. They got my on a shortlist and done on super short notice. Nancy was great with the booking as well!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zuetjZRVbHzKmuDXfPkVJEE_yVXGAa-f6bS-0FljYEQe7QNgwZbDsdCWjTSl8kDrcjSjEn1FCLO4-cgrx5lnEpc-b4h082pM3M599vTlxu1b9A-LEwTxru6mCJCaI1sp-iK7yPAYAsMyq=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-24"},{"Name":"Stephanie Laurie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhpG5GH68MPSUYm05dTj_sjoJXZIHjMoQJeO8MGggPps6ciX8oJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Dr. Kim here for the past 8 or 9 months. The first time was for an emergency root canal.  She and the rest of the team were very efficient, gentle, and great with explaining the procedure and checking on my comfort levels.\nThe last time was today for some front teeth fillings, and she was able to honor my cosmetic request to build on one of them a little to fill in a side gap I had developed from poor flossing habits. My smile looks SO much better.\nMy regular hygienist who does my cleanings is so sweet and kind, that it motivates me to keep up with my flossing.  I was honored to receive her praise after my cleaning yesterday.\nThe front desk team are also a wonderful bunch. Melinda has been so great and funny while I settle up my bills and schedule the next appointments.  Thank you to the whole office for everything!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Remi Calozza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHzSAHmbIpcGnM96JtDHQ8mrwpjhfjDuVXzVbQ41tdjpyCJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had my first appointment as a new patient at Capitol Hill Seattle Dentist, and it was a great experience from start to finish. The staff were friendly, welcoming, and made everything easy and efficient. Dr. Paul Sauvage was excellent — professional, attentive, and easy to talk to. He explained things clearly and made sure I was comfortable throughout the visit. As a new patient, I really appreciated how smooth and well-organized everything was. The office is clean and modern, and the whole team made a great impression. I’m glad I chose this practice and will definitely be returning. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Huston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9uPpTCJB66w0vAwUXb2zU9_E4vSMx_ImTXIEsEtKl6kALQw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr.Paul Sauvage and Dr. Anh Lao are both amazing! I felt so at ease with both of them. I have always been quite anxious going to the dentist, not anymore! They truly care about their patients. The entire staff is friendly and professional. They have made each visit easy and comfortable! I couldn’t ask for better dental care! Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JJ Oropeza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYxcPH0c6K9iOMlvmyFGuh3U53U_jZh2anygkBS5wczUtM1BmD9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great first time experience with the staff.\n\nFrom arriving and leaving Melinda did a fantastic job making sure everything at the front desk went smoothly. She was never rude or off-putting, which is most common with dental offices I have been to.\n\nJade was very easy going and it was like I forgot that I was at a dentist office for a minute there! Very kind and just felt like I was talking to a friend. Something you rarely get from a dental office.\n\nDr. Paul was very professional and caring with the procedure I received. He made me feel comfortable and not judged by the work that needed/needs to be done on my teeth. Which is so nice to get from a Dr. in this field.\n\nThis office is top tier and I actually look forward to coming back to continue the work that I need. Thank you to the staff that helped me today! You all are truly amazing and please continue to provide the service you did today. Forever going to recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Merrily Wyman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsWgs1fNz8ahfS7hw8MMU5-BjY4MIVZmyGvkZSTNeDKxieDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seattle's Capitol Hill Dentist provides great dental care. The office atmosphere is calming, the staff is attentive, and the dentist is both skilled and personable. They make preventative care a priority and explain everything clearly. I've never had to wait past my appointment time, which I greatly appreciate.\nBeth did an excellent job doing a super gentle cleaning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebecca Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2yJUuTF76lGIZ6nwPvCryjgBou-i1Q2nA4WNEFppkM-E_cgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Capitol Hill Dentist for years, and it's consistently been a fantastic experience. The location is incredibly convenient, the office is always spotless, and everything runs so efficiently. From the moment I walk in, I feel genuinely welcomed and well cared for. The team does an exceptional job with cleanings, and I have full trust in Dr. Linda Kim—her professionalism and warmth make all the difference. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a reliable and thoughtful dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
