he best office manager I’ve ever interacted with in the medical field. Guy reads minds. All the hygienists and doctors here are great at what they do and have good bedside manner. They work best if you provide info from your past doctors and visits to make sure everything connects up. Highly recommended. Even got myself a little going away gift !","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0L9zkvzsDL17zwnLVRrnwDg96N4MgeX_r7rvE9thshtTxSknosIEJSmUGp1VNoGfdfLe4kcwDF6IxVslRntZ42on8Tc2QxApqODDJ_-mDL5RysZ-kfE90AxBy62LsC6Rx8khmAXdOVu3qT=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-19"},{"Name":"Johnny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4D5fsS6ZY3pOGuxVbCuLtyFs6F5C63ic-5uEfqXBuaRTGlzc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Easy bus access in a nice part of Seattle. Older commercial building has been remodeled into a very modern clinic and waiting room. Pristine restrooms. Staff members and the doctor have great professional manner and work well together as a team. My teeth are getting great care. The billing and phone man is proficient and has nice people skills. Thank You Downtown Seattle Dentist.   Johnny Magnuson retired tugboat captain.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nahom Teages","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5UCiIGs4a-HZUMxuIGQ_YjBkqmF4qEVXIkCBCURBJktQ-qckm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"“I had an excellent experience at this dental clinic. The staff is incredibly friendly, professional, and welcoming from the moment you walk in. The dentist took time to explain everything clearly and made sure I was comfortable throughout the visit. The clinic is very clean, modern, and well-organized. I truly felt cared for and not rushed at all. Highly recommend this clinic to anyone looking for quality dental care!”","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0GYy7oRnlRDFMOPI05slbiPe-keOAo7MmPNrp2NuBdMSm_1eV_CZba45ZdjAi6O6FWymJFOGXK20gcXQ7Mbn7PXdKRF-I_AE8R5HZ0eDi22E_RHZ0AzYwekASFIwkV-lB5wFHJFX6tovRh=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13A4ZhN524C5Twp_PVmLtUktpQo6DIB9AFYzlFgMPqkaSs3APTOzoqcIp06MimGjuLljPt0tBg3VkLg6K_yf6wlBFGRWUizHMfxEMQsVHYPN0BrnA9K0pES20MPcw3YxtakoZRqvue83c=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-9"},{"Name":"strmcrsh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoSC4_U8Yi44yraHpNTyjKtEaD_mIePoplQnmrQkvgrqJJAsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dr Wilson was excellent, but since leaving, the overall experience has declined. Scheduling is confusing, and there’s no online system to view or manage appointments—you have to call and hope someone answers.\n\nThere seems to be frequent miscommunication between the front desk and the dental team. I’ve been booked for unnecessary or incorrect appointment types, and billing errors, including overcharging, which even had to be corrected by the dentist.\n\nRecent dental work was also disappointing. A filling I received wasn’t properly smoothed and had caused ongoing tooth pain. This office no longer feels as organized or professional as it once was, and you can find better care somewhere else","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean Hurlbut","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4iLpeXPEIzQxswkkCX6P2mh81MjRBLgU4cOsAbIe-XXs5FA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a sore tooth and they took me in the same day. They were accommodating and the front staff and hygienist were very friendly and knowledgeable. Got me in and out quick, would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Matuszewski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJCsR8H191xtBaezNiJNJnfQqzVdZ54PdBrkcIZMJuI7S2Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From Aaron at the front desk who always gets things off to a great start, to the assistant/hygienist to Dr Sabrina, this was an excellent visit. They all made what is typically a stressful trip one that was smooth and easy. Thanks to all!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justine Feilden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVb6tpxi48qsTKgJvL6bgoy7Tr110lM_PVBEW-J7TDjrbMpZz6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a checkup for myself and for my 20m old daughter. The team were absolutely amazing, and so helpful and caring with my little one so she wasn't afraid. Very professional and friendly too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AYAH SALAMA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj-4MEk3j36Wm_CNRvVQs7ulzkGqgkV_GlIStnrqnmKTNuBQtl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This office damaged my teeth, left me in pain, refused accountability, and hid behind “new management” — profit clearly comes before patient care.\n\nThe dentist Dr. Commons placed a filling so close to my nerve that I now can only chew on one side of my mouth, and even admitted I may need a root canal because of his work. After months of promising to resolve the issue and even exploring financial compensation for me, the office decided to refuse a refund and tried to hide behind “new management,” despite originally asking for my address to send the refund. They’ve made it clear they value profit over patient health. I used to love this office, I don’t know what happened to them. This was so unethical. I’ll be filing a formal complaint with the state dental board.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
