,"enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jacqueline Smith Armstrong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNPzuG8A8tbRy_AnDt-7BHIQEYgEuwmUzprK9inpPseUCsrDr-vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love visits to my Dental office.  My teeth are important and my smile is a big part of who I am.  From the moment I arrive, greeted by the front desk staff , Marnie \u0026 Jack are friendly and courteous Marnie \u0026 Jack. Minimal waiting time, I’m escorted to a comfortable room overlooking amazing view of Downtown Seattle.  In comes Shawn, who is the absolute best!  I nicknamed him The Professor!  While he is cleaning my teeth , he is giving me educational tips on dental care.  He handles dental instruments with precision!  He tells corny jokes and shares funny personal experiences! Once my appointment is completed, Jack or Marnie will validate my parking!  Such an awesome experience!   The best dental team in Seattle!!!  Big hugs to the entire Team.   Ya’ll see my smile?😃👍🏿💯♥️","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0UnFjv-L0-TYQ-PwUcPEZd7PmjWTiGTtNEu8Oq28PkczRmEZ5ut7_1iDuY1S2EcF4GSWtRsN8hgfVDNs5TX7i1VCDB8_B2K9UKsjtiew9NeAPcCDqUJ5nWKR8WJNG-tBP7PBd89pBrfZQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1a3sFD86pHbJKBSfFxEwcjvetRJIsnv0wd7L4nKNr4q9cggQtWVl5Ep7ZbTw2DnMKoWs7me1hTmnjW7Es7h714LRIZhuado6eThvfuXsyIOZMNArc1KfHpLjF_fpHod30o8ROurLX10uQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xS6VbZxJpD6QUnCpgwdhBAHWqgRjzkBswZJLT2E5koWTv4EatUj9en7GqxfY0PtRdM-RBWvEtPAaYPhnsqTplBHk8bwVvJk60bhcZbTrm8qxIQuYUTMnyoGcCHTA6YQ8GoMzKJZMBa80=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-20"},{"Name":"Kim Stirling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHnoYiNjyAhG7cTcA8pzY-wIGO5wT_Q4QtUMvSgmKeCaa0FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m always greeted with warm smiles and professionalism at Downtown Seattle Dentists! I’ve been going to this practice ever since moving to Seattle 3 years ago. I wouldn’t trust anyone else with my dental care. Top-notch, for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edward Nockles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4YjPnrfWvWblaALVUsWY-BpjtWAAm4UaweKNIAj1p-jJOM_5_pg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly impressed with the setup and space, but the staff is the real standout. As a new patient, the level of professionalism here makes me feel like I am in great hands. I have a procedure next week and feel completely confident that this review will not need editing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Selnekovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKABbMyMs8KK8MK3Rwn6eprJujVLc12Fk8oZhkx8qCORuOluw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Kim is amazing. Went in for a deep clean/scaling. She is such a professional with such a light touch. Truly painless and easy. The assistants are great and the front desk are so helpful and nice. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leslie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaZmXWB7sLFE3fR6CVrwkV8FG2NoGMlnhSezL-i1h0amcttg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a patient here for as long as I can remember and have always received excellent dental care. I especially want to recognize Marni at the front desk—she truly makes a difference. She always has a warm smile, remembers you, and makes you feel completely taken care of. She’s incredibly thorough and competent, and it genuinely feels like she’s invested in making sure you have the best possible experience. That kind of care and consistency feels rare these days, and Marni is such a breath of fresh air!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Gallagher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5AuCq3KMlF2MV43OCJAFqQb-kWxeVg46aNSReeamyzuEoSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really value this office, EVERY staff member is a gem: friendly, professional, social, focused on the task while still engaging in knowing me beyond my patient presence. Services are thorough, very communicative, HIGHLY recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKx6LSHUvzVwM80r_7Orr8aSTPnzVyjICQ7z5zoDTegWEJtUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience wit to ish Dr Kim \u0026 Winter, is always exceptional.  I'm pleased with their dental work.  They make a great team; the shots, the finished work plus Winter explains what's happening, which I like \u0026 want to know.\n\nThank you,\nTeresa Pitts\n05/08/1949","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Margaret Schaltenbrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWa8CZekVB8iy-k4I_6PGzm22sgj-Ys8fOMrcjzKZm35R-Lu-v8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Downtown Seattle Dentists for about 2 years now. I cannot emphasize enough how much I have appreciated being a patient here. My dental insurance was unexpectedly cancelled at the beginning of October and I only had coverage through the end of the month. Marnie and Jack were able to move things around so I could reschedule my cleaning (and subsequent filling!) before my insurance expired.\n\nI also had Invisalign treatment through their office and had a great experience. Dr. Grueske's explanation of the treatment plan and timeline provided an insightful, accurate description of what to expect.\n\nI am very happy with the results of my orthodontic treatment and regular dental care through DSD. Thank you, DSD team!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
